\id REV
\h Asargeb 
\toc1 Asargeb 
\toc2 Asargeb 
\toc3 Asa. 
\mt1 Asargeb  
\c 1
\s1 Tamezwarut  
\m
\v 1 Asargab n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ i d as iwca AREBBI, ḥima ad isscen i imsexxaren nnes min ittxeṣṣa ad imsar deɣya, uca issargeb i-t am t issekk s \add ufus n\add* lmalak nnes i umsexxar nnes Yuḥanna.  
\v 2 Wanita iched x Wawař n AREBBI u zi cchadet n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ u zi marra min iẓra,  
\v 3 \bd Sseɛd\bd* n wenni iqqaren d yinni ittesřan awařen n nnubuwa-ya u qqimen ttᵉṭṭfen di min daysen yuran, maɣar aqa řweqt tiweḍ-dd. \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Asa. 22:7, 10. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Yuḥanna, i sebɛa n tmesmunin di Asiya: Ad kidwem yiři arḍa d řehna zeg wenni iǧan d wenni tuɣa d wenni dd ɣa yasen, uřa zi sebɛa n Arruḥat nni iǧan zzat i řɛarc nnes, \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Uf. 3:14; Asa. 1:8; 4:8; 11:17; 16:5. \x*  
\v 5 u zi Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, Acehhad amtiqqi, Amenzu n imettinen d Ameqqran n ijeǧiden n temmurt. \add I\add* wenni d aneɣ ittexsen u d aneɣ ifekken zi ddnub nneɣ s Idammen nnes, \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Ica. 55:4; Řex. 20:28; 1 Kur. 15:20; Kul. 1:18; Ɛbr. 9:12, 14; 1 Bṭ. 1:19; 1 Yḥ. 1:7; Asa. 3:14; 5:9. \x*  
\v 6 d wenni yarr aneɣ d ict n Tagelda n ikehhanen ɣar AREBBI d Babas, i Netta ad ɣares yiři uɛuǧi d ṣṣulṭa i řebda qaɛ. Amin! \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Rum. 12:1; 1 Bṭ. 2:5, 9; Asa. 5:10. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 Xzar, Netta ad dd-yas ak-d iseynuten, kuř tiṭṭ ad t tẓar, uřa d inni t issnuqqben. Marra tiqebbař n temmurt ad xas wtent agejdur. Wah, amin! \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Dan. 7:13; Zak. 12:10; Mt. 24:30; 25:31; Yḥ. 19:37; Řex. 1:11; 1 Ts. 1:10; 2 Ts. 1:10; Yah. 14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Necc d Alif d Taw, \add Amezwaru d Uneggaru\add*, iqqar SIDI AREBBI, d wenni iǧan d wenni tuɣa d wenni dd ɣa yasen, Amzemmar x kuřci. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Ica. 41:4; 44:6; Asa. 21:6; 22:13. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aḍhar n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ  
\m
\v 9 Necc, Yuḥanna, umatwem d umɛacar nwem di řmeḥnet u di ṣṣbar nni iǧan di Yasuɛ, tuɣa ayi di tegzirt qqaren as Batmus di ṭṭweɛ n Wawař n AREBBI d cchadet n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.  
\v 10 Usiɣ-dd di Arruḥ deg wass amezwaru n ssimana uca sřiɣ awarni ayi ict n tmijja tejhed am \bd usuḍi deg uyicc n ucarri\bd*, \f ◼ \fr 1:10 \ft \+fk deg wass amezwaru n ssimana\ft  - aqa-t deg wass n Umensi Iqeddsen n Arebbi umi ttidaren řmuminin (di mkuř ssimana) řmewt n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ di tmesmunin.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Asa. 4:2. \x*  
\v 11 teqqar: “Min tᵉttwařid, ari t deg ijj n wedlis \add ittwanḍen\add*, ssekk i-tt-i-dd i sebɛa n tmesmunin: ɣar Afasus, ɣar Smirna, ɣar Pirɣamus, ɣar Tiyatira, ɣar Sardis, ɣar Filadilfiya uca ɣar Layudikiya.”   
\m
\v 12 Xenni nnqeřbeɣ, ḥima ad ssneɣ wi kidi issawařen. Ařami nnqeřbeɣ, ẓriɣ sebɛa n řeqnadeř n wureɣ.  
\v 13 Di řwesṭ n řeqnadeř ijjen am Mmis n bnadem, tuɣa yarḍ apalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* u ɣares ijj n webyas n wureɣ x idmaren. \x ◘ \xo 1:13 \xt Ḥiz. 1:26; Dan. 7:13; Asa. 14:14. \x*  
\v 14 Azeǧif nnes d ucuwwaf nnes tuɣa aten d icemřařen am taḍuft, am wedfeř, uca tiṭṭawin nnes am yiḥudaq n tmessi, \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Dan. 7:9; Asa. 19:12. \x*  
\v 15 iḍaren nnes am nnḥas zi Lubnan, iḥman deg ufarran, u řḥess nnes am řḥess n waṭṭas n waman. \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Asa. 14:2. \x*  
\v 16 Tuɣa ɣares deg ufus nnes afusi sebɛa n yetran uca zeg uqemmum nnes itteffeɣ-dd zzayes lansa iqḍeɛ uca aɣembub nnes am tfuct s jjehd nnes. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Ica. 49:2; Afa. 6:17; Ɛbr. 4:12; Asa. 2:16; 19:15. \x*   
\m
\v 17 Ařami t ẓriɣ, wḍiɣ as ɣar iḍaren nnes axmi mmuteɣ uca Netta issars xafi afus nnes afusi, inna: “War tteggʷed ca! Aqa Necc d Amezwaru d Uneggaru, \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt Ica. 41:4; 44:6; 48:12. \x*  
\v 18 Necc d wenni iddaren, u Necc tuɣa mmuteɣ, u xzar, aqa Necc d wenni iddaren i řebda qaɛ! Aqa ɣari tsarut n řmewt d řaxart. \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt Ayub 12:14; Ica. 22:22; Rum. 6:9; Asa. 3:7; 20:1. \x*  
\v 19 S uyenni ari min teẓrid uřa d timesřayin nni iǧan d timesřayin nni i ɣa imsaren awarni man aya.  
\v 20 Aqa ssirr n sebɛa n itran i teẓrid deg ufus inu afusi u \add ssirr\add* n sebɛa n řeqnadeř n wureɣ d wa: sebɛa n itran aqa aten d lmalakat n sebɛa n tmesmunin uca sebɛa n řeqnadeř, aqa aten d sebɛa n tmesmunin.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Tibratin i sebɛa n tmesmunin  
\m
\v 1 \bd Ari i lmalak di tmesmunt n Afasus!\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar wenni ɣar iǧa sebɛa n itran deg ufus nnes, wenni igguren di řwesṭ n sebɛa n řeqnadeř n wureɣ:  
\v 2 ‘Necc ssneɣ řexdayem nnec d warbar nnec d ṣṣbar nnec, belli war tzemmared ad tḥemřed inni iɛeffnen uca tqeǧbed inni itteggen ixef nsen d rrusul, maca war ǧin ca, uca tufid ten d ayt n bu-ixarriqen. \f ◼ \fr 2:2 \ft \+fk rrusul\ft  - niɣ ‘imazanen’.\f*  
\v 3 Cek tṣebbared u teksid armeḥ x ssibbet n Yisem inu u war tuḥiřed ca.  
\v 4 Maca ɣari xak ca, belli tejjid tayri nnec tamezwarut.  
\v 5 Ɛqeř manis-dd tewḍid uca tub, xenni egg řexdayem timezwura! Mařa war iǧi amenni, ad ɣarek dd-aseɣ deɣya, ad kesseɣ řqendiř nnec, mařa war tᵉttubed ca.  
\v 6 Maca man aya tiwḍed, aqa tcarrhed řexdayem n ayt n Inikulayiten, tinni carrheɣ uřa d Necc. \f ◼ \fr 2:6 \ft \+fk Inikulayiten\ft  - nitni d iwdan nni iffɣen zeg webrid n l'iman di Lmasiḥ (Xẓar Asa. 2:6; 2:15)\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Asa. 2:6. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen, ejj i-t ad iseř min iqqar Arruḥ i tmesmunin.  
\m Wenni i ɣa iɣellben ad t ssecceɣ zi Tcejjart n Tudart i yeǧan di jjennet n AREBBI.’” \f ◼ \fr 2:7 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt Amz. 2:9; Asa. 22:2. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 \bd Ari i lmalak n tmesmunt n Smirna!\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar wenni d Amezwaru d Uneggaru, Wenni immuten uca iddar: \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Ica. 41:4; 44:6; Asa. 1:17. \x*  
\v 9 ‘Aqa ssneɣ řmeḥnet nnec d wezřaḍ nnec, qaɛ amenni cek tᵉttejjared, u \add aqa-yi ssneɣ\add* uřa d aceqqef n yinni iqqaren aqa aten d Udayen s tidett, maca nitni war ǧin ca \add d Udayen\add*, maca d tamzida n cciṭan.  
\v 10 War tteggʷed ca zi min ɣa tᵉttwaɛeddbed. Aqa ibřis ad inḍar \add ca\add* zzaywem di řeḥbes, ḥima ad tᵉttwajarrbem. Ad ɣarwem tiři řmeḥnet n ɛecra n wussan. Iřim d imtiqqan ař řmewt, řexdenni ad awem wceɣ ttaj n Tudart.   
\m
\v 11 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen, ejj i-t ad iseř min iqqar Arruḥ i tmesmunin.  
\m Wenni i ɣa iɣellben war d as dd-tᵉttiwi ca txessart zi řmewt wiss tnayen.’” \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Mt. 13:9. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 \bd Ari i lmalak di tmesmunt n Pirɣamus!\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar wenni ɣar iǧa ssif iqḍeɛ x tnayen n wudmawen: \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Asa. 1:16; 2:16. \x*  
\v 13 ‘Necc ssneɣ mani tzeddɣed, \add diha mani ittbedda\add* řɛarc n cciṭan. Aqa teqqimed tᵉṭṭfed deg Yisem inu uca war tenkared ca l’iman dayi, Uca deg wussan umi tuɣa cek tᵉttmenɣed \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ucehhad amtiqqi inu di ṭṭweɛ n marra icehhaden inu imtiqqan, aqa ittwaneɣ netta jar awem.  
\v 14 Maca ɣari xak ca, minzi ɣarek dinni \add ca\add* inni itteṭṭfen deg useřmed n Balɛam, wenni tuɣa issřemden i Balak mammec ɣa inḍar taɛenkrift i ayt n Israil, ḥima ad ccen zi min ɣarṣen i l’aṣnam uca ad sefssaden ixef nsen. \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Řxř. 22:23; 24:14; 25:1; 31:16. \x*  
\v 15 Ɣarek din ɛawed \add ca\add* inni itteṭṭfen di tɣuri n Inikulayiten. \f ◼ \fr 2:15 \ft \+fk Inikulayiten\ft  - nitni d iwdan nni iffɣen zeg webrid n l'iman di Lmasiḥ (Xẓar Asa. 2:6; 2:15)\f*  
\v 16 S uyenni tub! Mařa war iǧi amenni, ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ deɣya, ad kisen mmenɣeɣ s ssif n uqemmum inu. \x ◘ \xo 2:16 \xt Ica. 49:2; Afa. 6:17; Ɛbr. 4:12; Asa. 1:16. \x*   
\m
\v 17 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen, ejj i-t ad iseř min iqqar Arruḥ i tmesmunin.  
\m Wenni i ɣa iɣellben ad as ssecceɣ ‘manna’ innufaren uca ad as wceɣ ijj n uqayas d acemřař, uca x uqayas nni ittwari xas ijj n isem n jdid, war t issin ḥed mɣir wenni t iṭṭfen.’” \x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt Uf. 16:4-36. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 Ari i lmalak \bd di tmesmunt n Tiyatira!\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar Mmis n AREBBI wenni ɣar iǧa tiṭṭawin am yiḥudaq n tmessi d iḍaren nnes am nnḥas zi Lubnan: \x ◘ \xo 2:18 \xt Asa. 1:14, 15. \x*  
\v 19 ‘Necc ssneɣ řexdayem nnec uřa d tayri nnec d l’iman nnec d tsexxart nnec d ṣṣbar nnec, aqa řexdayem nnec tineggura imɣaren x tmezwura.  
\v 20 Maca ɣari xak aṭṭas, minzi tejjid tameṭṭut nnec Izabil, tenni iqqaren belli nettat d tanabit, tesseřmad uca tessɣekkʷa imsexxaren inu, ḥima ad ssfesden ixef nsen uca ad ccen min ittwaɣarṣen i l’aṣnam. \x ◘ \xo 2:20 \xt 1 Ij. 16:31; 2 Ij. 9:7. \x*  
\v 21 Aqa wciɣ as ca n řweqt ḥima ad tᵉtub, \add maca\add* nettat war tᵉttexs ca ad tᵉtub zi farq-ccɣeř nnes.  
\v 22 Xzar, ad tt ɣeḍřeɣ di tassut, \add ad tiři teḥřec ař řmewt\add*, uca inni akides izennan, \add ad ten nedheɣ\add* di řmeḥnet tameqqrant mařa war tuben ca zi min ggin.  
\v 23 Tarwa nnes ad ten wteɣ s řmewt uca marra timesmunin ad fehment aqa Necc d wenni iqeǧben tiẓẓař d wuřawen uca ad wceɣ i kuř ijjen zzaywem anect n řexdayem nwem. \x ◘ \xo 2:23 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:7; 1 Im. 28:9; 29:17; Izhd.7:10; 62:13; Irm. 11:20; 17:10; 32:19; Mt. 16:27; Řex. 1:24; Rum. 2:6; 14:12; 2 Kur. 5:10; Gal. 6:5; Asa. 20:12. \x*  
\v 24 Maca i kenniw u i inneɣni di Tiyatira - \add ixs ad yini\add* i marra inni war ɣar teǧi ca taɣuri-ya, war ssinen umi qqaren nitni ‘řaǧaɣ n cciṭan’ - ad awem iniɣ: Necc war xawem ttdarraceɣ ca taɣrart nneɣnit.  
\v 25 \add Maca\add* min ɣarwem, ṭṭfem dayes ař dd ɣa yaseɣ. \x ◘ \xo 2:25 \xt Asa. 3:11. \x*   
\m
\v 26 Wenni i ɣa iɣellben u wenni i ɣa iṭṭfen di řexdayem inu, ad as wceɣ ṣṣulṭa x řegnus  
\v 27 maḥend ad ten yarwes s uzeǧaḍ n wuzzař, ad ten tarẓim am iɣarrafen n bu-třaxt, am mammec i tᵉṭṭfeɣ uřa d Necc zi Baba, \x ◘ \xo 2:27 \xt Izhd. 2:8-9. \x*  
\v 28 uca Necc ad as wceɣ itri n řefjar.   
\m
\v 29 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen, ejj i-t ad iseř min iqqar Arruḥ i tmesmunin.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\m
\v 1 \bd Ari i lmalak di tmesmunt n Sardis!\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar wenni ɣar iǧa sebɛa n Arruḥat n AREBBI d sebɛa n yetran:  
\m ‘Necc ssneɣ řexdayem nnec, aqa ɣarek isem, belli aqa teddared, \add maca\add* cek aqa tᵉttmettid. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Asa. 1:14, 16. \x*  
\v 2 Ḥḍa, sejhed min iqqimen, inni tenwid cek ad ten tᵉttejjid ad tᵉmmtem, maɣar ufiɣ aqa řexdayem nnec war kemmřent ca ɣar AREBBI.  
\v 3 Ɛqeř mliḥ, mammec \add xas\add* tesřid u mammec tᵉṭṭfed, ḥḍa uca tub! Maca mařa war tᵉttfiqed, ad ɣarek dd-aseɣ am uceffar, war tessined ca di man tasaɛɛet i xak dd ɣa beddeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt Mt. 24:43; 1 Ts. 5:2; 2 Bṭ. 3:10; Asa. 3:19; 16:15. \x*  
\v 4 Maca ɣari ca n ismawen di Sardis, inni war issxemjen ca arruḍ nsen uca nitni gguren zzati s \add warruḍ\add* d acemřař, minzi nitni sdaheǧen t.   
\m
\v 5 Wenni i ɣa iɣellben ammu, ad as yarḍen arruḍ d acemřař. Ɛemmarṣ ad kkseɣ isem nnes zeg Wedlis ittwanḍen n Tudart, maca ad cehdeɣ x yisem nnes zzat i Baba d lmalakat nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Uf. 32:32; Izhd. 69:29; Mt. 10:32; Lk. 12:8; Fil. 4:3; Asa. 20:12; 21:27. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen, ejj i-t ad iseř min iqqar Arruḥ i tmesmunin.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 7 \bd Ari i lmalak n tmesmunt n Filadilfiya!\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar Umqeddas wenni d Tidett d wenni ɣar iǧa tsarut n Dawud d wenni i ɣa yarezmen, \add xenni\add* uřa d ijjen ad ibelleɛ, d wenni i ɣa ibellɛen, \add xenni\add* uřa d ijjen ad yarzem: \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt Ayub 12:14; Ica. 22:22; Asa. 1:18; 3:14. \x*   
\m
\v 8 ‘Necc ssneɣ řexdayem nnec. Xzar, Necc ggiɣ zzatec ict n tewwart tarzem, tenni uřa d ijj war izemmar ad tt ibelleɛ, minzi waxxa jjehd nnec d ameẓyan, qaɛ amenni teḥḍid Awař inu uca war tenkared ca Isem inu.  
\v 9 Xzar, ad wceɣ ca zi temzida n cciṭan, inni iqqaren aqa nitni d Udayen, \add maca\add* nitni war ǧin ca amenni, maca nitni ssxarriqen. Xzar, ad ten arreɣ ad ac wḍan ɣar iḍaren nnec. Nitni ad neɛmen belli Necc ssɛizzeɣ cek. \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Asa. 2:9. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Minzi aqa cek teḥḍid Awař inu n ṣṣbar, ad xak ḥḍiɣ ɛawed zi \add tsaɛɛet n\add* ujarreb tenni i d ɣa yasen x temmurt marra i ujarreb n yinni izeddɣen x temmurt.  
\v 11 Necc ad dd-aseɣ deɣya. Ṭṭef di min ɣarek, ḥima uřa d ijj war d ac ittekkes ca ttaj nnec. \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Asa. 2:25. \x*   
\m
\v 12 Wenni i ɣa iɣellben ad t ggeɣ d apilar di Zzawect Tameqqrant n AREBBI uca war zzayes ittwammeksi ɛemmarṣ. Necc ad xas ariɣ Isem n AREBBI inu d yisem n tendint n jdid, Urcalim i dd ɣa ihwan zeg ujenna zi AREBBI inu, uřa d Isem inu n jdid. \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt 1 Ij. 7:21; Asa. 21:2, 10; 22:4. \x*   
\m
\v 13 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen, ejj i-t ad iseř min iqqar Arruḥ i tmesmunin.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 14 \bd Ari i lmalak n tmesmunt n Layudikiya\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar wenni d Amin, Acehhad amtiqqi d tidett, wenni d beddu n marra min dd-ixřeq AREBBI: \x ◘ \xo 3:14 \xt Kul. 1:15; Asa. 1:5, 6. \x*   
\m
\v 15 ‘Necc ssneɣ řexdayem nnec, aqa cek war tesmiḍed war teḥmid. Meɛlik beɛda tsemḍed niɣ teḥmid!  
\v 16 S uyenni, umi cek temřuded, war teḥmid, war tesmiḍed, ad cek ɛuqqeɣ zeg uqemmum inu.  
\v 17 Minzi cek teqqared: Necc ɣari agřa uca immarni-dd ɣari wagřa, war d ayi ittxeṣṣi walu, \add am\add* war tessined ca belli aqa cek tḥeřced u dayek řeɣben d zzeřḍ u aqa cek d adarɣař d aɛaryan,  
\v 18 ad cek neṣḥeɣ maḥend ad xafi tesɣed wureɣ iqquren, ikkin timessi, ḥima ad tdewřed d bu-wagřa, uřa d arruḍ d acemřař, ḥima ad t tyarḍed u war teqqim tḍehhar ɛad řefḍiḥet n tuɛɛaryent nnec. U dhen \add ɛawed\add* ddhen x tiṭṭawin nnec maḥend ad taf tettwařid. \x ◘ \xo 3:18 \xt 2 Kur. 5:3; Asa. 7:13; 16:15; 19:8. \x*  
\v 19 Marra wenni ssɛizzeɣ, ttwebbxeɣ t u arebbiɣ t. Xenni cḍar, tub! \x ◘ \xo 3:19 \xt Ayub 5:17; Awřn. 3:12; Ɛbr. 12:5. \x*  
\v 20 Aqa da, Necc beddeɣ ɣar tewwart, ssqarqubeɣ-dd. Mařa isřa ḥed i tmijja inu, ad yarzem tawwart, Necc ad ɣares adfeɣ uca ad kis mmunesweɣ d netta akidi.   
\m
\v 21 Wenni i ɣa iɣellben ad as wceɣ, ḥima ad iqqim akidi x řɛarc inu, am Necc ɣellbeɣ uca qqimeɣ ak-d Baba x řɛarc nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:21 \xt Mt. 19:28; 1 Kur. 6:2. \x*   
\m
\v 22 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen, ejj i-t ad iseř min iqqar Arruḥ i tmesmunin.’” *   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Řɛarc deg ujenna  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya, xzar, ict n tewwart tennurzem deg ujenna. Uca tmijja i sřiɣ akidi dd-issawařen am yijj n \bd usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri\bd*, tenna: “Geɛɛed da, \add xenni\add* Necc ad ac ssecneɣ min ggur ad imsar awarni man aya.”   
\m
\v 2 Řexdenni ireḥḥef ayi-dd Arruḥ, u xzar, ijj n řɛarc ibedd deg ujenna, tuɣa Netta iqqim xas.  
\v 3 U tifras n Wenni \add xas\add* iqqimen am \add weẓru n\add* yaspis d sardiyus, uca tasřit n wenẓar n iseynuten i-dd-ittennḍen i řɛarc iḍhar am \add weẓru n\add* smaraxt.   
\m
\v 4 Quwwaren as i řɛarc arebɛa u ɛicrin n řekrasi igellden uca arebɛa u-ɛicrin n imɣaren tuɣa qqimen x řekrasi igellden, arḍen arruḍ d acemřař, ɣarsen x uzeǧif ttijan n wureɣ.   
\m
\v 5 Uca zi řɛarc nni tteffɣen-dd zzayes wajjajen d assamen d tmijjawin. Zzat i řɛarc areqqen sebɛa n iṣefḍawen, tina d sebɛa n Arruḥat n AREBBI.   
\m
\v 6 Ɣar zzat n řɛarc tuɣa din ijj n řebḥar n zzaj, igga am akristal. Di řwesṭ n řɛarc d min d as dd-innḍen tuɣa din arebɛa n imuddaren, ɛemmaren s tiṭṭawin marra ɣar zzat d ḍeffar. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt Uf. 24:10; Asa. 15:2. \x*  
\v 7 Amuddar amezwaru yarwes deg wayrad, ameddar wiss tnayen yarwes deg uɛejmi, ameddar wiss třata tuɣa aɣembub nnes axmi n bnadem uca amuddar wiss arebɛa yarwes deg ugider iṭṭawen.  
\v 8 Kuř ijjen zi arebɛa n imuddaren tuɣa ibedd, tteffɣen-dd zeg waccaren nnes d sennej setta n wafriwen i dd as dd-innḍen, ɛemmaren s tiṭṭawin ɣar daxeř. Nitni war ẓrin arraḥet ass d ǧiřet, nnan:  
\b  
\m \qt “Amqeddas, amqeddas,\qt*  
\m \qt amqeddas d SIDI AREBBI,\qt*  
\m \qt Amzemmar x kuřci\qt*  
\m \qt d wenni tuɣa, d wenni iǧan,\qt*  
\m \qt d wenni dd ɣa yasen.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Ica. 6:3; Asa. 1:4, 8; 11:17; 16:5. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Uca xmi ɣa wcen arebɛa n imuddaren aɛuǧi d ccan d uqadi i wenni iqqimen x řɛarc, d wenni iddaren i řebda qaɛ - “Amin!” -  
\v 10 \add xenni\add* arebɛa u ɛicrin n imɣaren wḍan ɣar temmurt ɣar zzat n wenni iqqimen x řɛarc, sejden i wenni iddaren i řebda qaɛ - “Amin!” - uca ssarsen ttijan nsen ɣar zzat i řɛarc, nnan:   
\b  
\m
\v 11 \qt “Cek, a Siditneɣ d AREBBI nneɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt tesdaheǧed ad teksid\qt*  
\m \qt aɛuǧi d ccan d jjehd,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar Cek d wenni iggin marra timesřayin-a,\qt*  
\m \qt u aqa atent din\qt*  
\m \qt u ttwaxeřqent s řxaḍar nnec!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Asa. 5:12. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Adlis ittwannḍen d Yezmar  
\m
\v 1 Uca ẓriɣ ɣar ufus afusi n wenni iqqimen x řɛarc ijj n Wedlis \add ittwanḍen\add*, tuɣa xas tira ɣar daxeř d barra, uca \add Adlis\add* tuɣa ittwacemmeɛ s sebɛa n icemmiɛen. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt Ḥiz. 2:10. \x*  
\v 2 Uca ẓriɣ ijj n lmalak ijhed nneɣni, ittřaɣa s jjehd:  
\b  
\m \qt “Man wen isdaheǧen ad yarzem\qt*  
\m \qt Adlis-a \+tl ittwannḍen\+tl*\qt*,  
\m \qt uca ad ikkes icemmiɛen nnes?”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 Uca uřa d ijj deg ujenna niɣ di temmurt niɣ sadu temmurt izemmar ad yarzem Adlis-a \add ittwannḍen\add* u ad ikkes icemmiɛen nnes, ad dayes ixzar. \x ◘ \xo 5:3 \xt Fil. 2:10; Asa. 5:13. \x*  
\v 4 Necc ruɣ aṭṭas umi war ufin wi isdaheǧen ad yarzem Adlis-a \add ittwannḍen\add* u ad yarzem icemmiɛen nnes.  
\v 5 Ijjen zeg imɣaren inna ayi: “War ttru ca! Xzar, Ayrad zi teqbič n Yahuda, Aẓwar n Dawud, aqa iɣelleb, ḥima ad yarzem Adlis-a \add ittwannḍen\add* d icemmiɛen nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Amz. 49:9, 10; Ica. 11:10; Rum. 15:12; Asa. 22:16. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Uca ẓriɣ di řwesṭ n řɛarc d arebɛa n imuddaren uca di řwesṭ n imɣaren, ijj n Izmar ibedd, igga axmi d taɣarṣt. Netta ɣares sebɛa n waccawen d sebɛa n tiṭṭawin, nitni d sebɛa n Arruḥat n AREBBI inni dd-ittwassekken ɣar ddunect tmun. \f ◼ \fr 5:6 \ft \+fk ddunect\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘temmurt’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Zak. 3:9; 4:10; Asa. 4:5. \x*  
\v 7 Aqa Netta yusa-dd uca iksi Adlis \add ittwannḍen\add* zeg ufus n wenni iqqimen x řɛarc.   
\m
\v 8 Ařami iṭṭef Adlis \add ittwannḍen\add*, wḍan-dd arebɛa n imuddaren d arebɛa u-ɛicrin n imɣaren ɣar temmurt zzat i Yezmar. Nitni marra idsen ɣarsen ict n lharpa d ijj n ṭṭebṣi n wureɣ iccur s řebxur: man aya d tiẓaǧitin n imqeddasen. \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Izhd. 141:2; Asa. 14:2. \x*  
\v 9 Uca ttɣennajen ijj n izři n jdid, qqaren:  
\b  
\m \qt “Cek tesdaheǧed\qt*  
\m \qt ad teksid Adlis \+tl ittwannḍen\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt ad tekksed icemmiɛen nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi Cek tᵉttwaɣarṣed\qt*  
\m \qt uca s Idammen nnec\qt*  
\m \qt tesɣid aneɣ i AREBBI,\qt*  
\m \qt zi kuř taqbič d řgens d cceɛb.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 5:9 \xt Řex. 20:28; Afa. 1:7; Kul. 1:14; Ɛbr. 9:12; 10:10; 1 Bṭ. 1:19; 1 Yḥ. 1:7; Asa. 4:11. \x*   
\m
\v 10 \qt ”Cek tarrid ten d ict n tgelda\qt*  
\m \qt n ikehhanen d ijeǧiden\qt*  
\m \qt i AREBBI nneɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt u nitni ad ḥekmen\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl am ijeǧiden\+tl* x temmurt.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Uf. 19:6; 1 Bṭ. 2:5, 9; Asa. 1:6. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Xenni ẓriɣ, uca sřiɣ tmijja n waṭṭas n lmalakat nnḍent i řɛarc uřa n imuddaren d imɣaren, uca tuɣa atent ɛecra-ařaf di ɛecra n řuřuf u ařaf di řuřuf, \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Dan. 7:10; Ɛbr. 12:22. \x*  
\v 12 qqaren s tmijja ijehden:  
\b  
\m \qt “Izmar nni ittwaɣarṣen\qt*  
\m \qt isdaheǧ ad iṭṭef\qt*  
\m \qt ṣṣulṭa d wagřa d tiɣit,\qt*  
\m \qt d jjehd d ccan d uɛuǧi,\qt*  
\m \qt d lbaraka!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt Asa. 4:11. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Uca kuř ijj i dd-ixeřqen deg ujenna u x temmurt d sadu temmurt u x řebḥar, \add wah,\add* qaɛ min iǧan daysen, sřiɣ asen, qqaren:  
\b  
\m \qt “Lbaraka d ccan d uɛuǧi d ṣṣulṭa\qt*  
\m \qt ad iřin i wenni iqqimen x řɛarc\qt*  
\m \qt u i Yezmar i řebda qaɛ!”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Uca umi arebɛa n imuddaren nnan: “Amin!”, wḍan imɣaren ɣar temmurt, sejden.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Sebɛa n icemmiɛen  
\m
\v 1 Uca ẓriɣ umi Izmar ifsi \bd ijjen zi sebɛa n icemmiɛen\bd*, uca sřiɣ i yijjen zi arebɛa n imuddaren iqqar s tmijja am wajjaj: “As-dd, xzar!”  
\v 2 Xenni sřiɣ u ẓriɣ, u xzar ijj n \bd uyis d acemřař\bd*, d wenni xas inyin ɣares ijj n řqewṣ \add n fřitca\add* uca immewc as ijj n ttaj uca iffeɣ-dd, iɣřeb, ittɣellab, u maḥend ad iɣřeb. \x ◘ \xo 6:2 \xt Asa. 19:11. \x*   
\m
\v 3 Ařami yarzem \bd acemmiɛ wiss tnayen\bd*, sřiɣ i umuddar wiss tnayen, iqqar: “As-dd!”  
\v 4 Uca iffeɣ-dd ijj n \bd uyis d azeggʷaɣ\bd*, uca wenni xas inyin, ggin t ḥima ad ikkes řehna x temmurt, ḥima ad kkaren iwdan ad ɣarṣen i wayawya uca immewc as ijj n ssif imɣar.   
\m
\v 5 Ařami yarzem \bd acemmiɛ wiss třata\bd*, sřiɣ i umuddar wiss třata iqqar: “As-dd!” Xzar, ijj n \bd uyis d abarcan\bd*, d wenni xas inyin ɣares ijj n řmizan deg ifassen nnes.  
\v 6 Zi řwesṭ n imuddaren sřiɣ i yict n tmijja teqqar: “Ijj n řmud n yirden s yijj n dinar u třata n řemdud n imendi s yijj n dinar, u zzect d binu war ten ttḍiyyiɛem ca!” \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt Asa. 9:4. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Ařami yarzem \bd acemmiɛ wiss arebɛa\bd*, sřiɣ i tmijja n umuddar \add wiss arebɛa\add* teqqar: “As-dd!”  
\v 8 Uca ẓriɣ ijj n \bd uyis d asnabi\bd*, d wenni xas inyin, qqaren as ‘Řmewt’, uca teḍfar i-t řaxart. Temmewc as ṣṣulṭa x ijj n arbeɛ n temmurt ḥima ad nɣen s ssif, s řaẓ, s řmewt u s řewḥuc n temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 6:8 \ft \+fk asnabi\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘awraɣ aceḥcaḥ’ niɣ ‘awraɣ adardas’.\f*   
\m
\v 9 Ařami yarzem \bd acemmiɛ wiss xemsa\bd*, ẓriɣ sadu uɛalṭar řeɛmur n yinni ittwanɣen di ṭṭweɛ n Wawař n AREBBI u di ṭṭweɛ n cchadet n Yasuɛ i tuɣa ɣarsen. \x ◘ \xo 6:9 \xt Asa. 19:10; 20:4. \x*  
\v 10 Nitni řaɣan s jjehd, nnan: “\add A\add* SIDI, \add a\add* Amqeddas d Bab n tidett, mecḥař i ɣa teqqimed war tḥekkmed, war tᵉttneqmed ca i idammen nneɣ zeg inni izeddɣen di temmurt?”  
\v 11 Uca wcin i kuř ijjen zzaysen řeɛbayat d ticemřařin, u ittwanna asen belli ad areyyḥen drus n řweqt ař ɣa ikemmeř lɛadad n imsexxaren imɛacaren nsen d wawmaten nsen, inni i ɣa ittwanɣen ɛawed am nitni.   
\m
\v 12 Uca ẓriɣ ařami yarzem \bd acemmiɛ wiss setta\bd*, aqa imsar ijj n wenhezzi n temmurt d ameqqran u tafuct tedweř d tabarcant amecnaw ict n txancet n wecḍan uca taziri tmun tegga amecnaw idammen, \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt Řex. 2:20. \x*  
\v 13 uca itran n ujenna wḍan-dd ɣar temmurt am wartu immenḍar iqurraɛ nnes xmi t-i-dd-iɣeṭṭeř ijj n usemmiḍ d ameqqran. \f ◼ \fr 6:13 \ft \+fk itran n ujenna\ft  - ixs ad yini lmalakat inni iwḍan ak-d cciṭan. Xzar Asa. 12:4, 9.\f*  
\v 14 Ittwafeǧqen ijenwan uca ttwanḍen nitni am mammec \add nneḍen\add* idlisen. Uca kuř adrar d marra tigzirin ttwakksen zeg imucan nsen.  
\v 15 Ijeǧiden n temmurt d imeqqranen d yinni d izeǧifen x wařef d aytbab n wagřa d yinni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa d kuř ismeɣ d aḥurri, aqa nitni \add marra\add* ssnuffaren ixef nsen deg ifran u jar řejruf n idurar, \x ◘ \xo 6:15 \xt Ica. 2:20\x*  
\v 16 nnan i idurar d řejruf: “Wḍam-dd xaneɣ, ffarem aneɣ zeg wudem n Izmar, \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt Ica. 2:17-21; Ḥuc. 10:8; Lk. 23:30; Asa. 9:6. \x*  
\v 17 minzi ass ameqqran n weɣḍab nnes aqa yusa-dd, man wen izemmaren ad iqqim ibedd!” \x ◘ \xo 6:17 \xt Yuw. 2:10, 31; 3:15; Ica. 13:6-13; 24:23; Am. 8:9; Mt. 24:29; Řex. 2:20; Asa. 6:12-13\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Acemmiɛ n Arebbi iddaren  
\m
\v 1 Awarni man aya ẓriɣ arebɛa n lmalakat beddent ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura n temmurt, ṭṭfent arebɛa n isemmiḍen n temmurt, ḥima war ittsuḍi usemmiḍ řa x řbarr řa x waman uřa x ca n tcejjart. \f ◼ \fr 7:1 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  
\v 2 Uca ẓriɣ ijj n lmalak nneɣni yuři-dd manis d tneqqar tfuct, aqa ɣares acemmiɛ n AREBBI iddaren uca iřaɣa s jjehd i arebɛa n lmalakat nni umi temmewc tzemmar ḥima ad ssexsarent tammurt d řebḥar, \x ◘ \xo 7:2 \xt Yḥ. 6:26; Asa. 9:4.\x*  
\v 3 iqqar: “War ttsexsarem tammurt uřa d řebḥar uřa d ticejjura ař ɣa negg acemmiɛ x tenyarin n imsexxaren n AREBBI nneɣ.”   
\m
\v 4 Uca sřiɣ řqedd n yinni ittwacemmɛen, mya u-arebɛa u-rebɛin-ařef aqa ttwacemmɛen zi marra tiqebbař n Israil: \x ◘ \xo 7:4 \xt Asa. 14:1. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Yahuda,  
\m tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Rubin,  
\m tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Jad,   
\m
\v 6 tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Acir,  
\m tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Naftali,  
\m tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Manassa,   
\m
\v 7 tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Cimɛun,  
\m tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Issakar,  
\m tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Lawi,   
\m
\v 8 tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Zibulun,  
\m tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Yusuf,  
\m tenɛac-ařef zi teqbič n Binyamin.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řɣaci ameqqran zi řegnus  
\m
\v 9 Awarni man aya aqa ẓriɣ ijj n ubarru n řɣaci ameqqran i war izemmar uřa d ijj ad t iḥseb, zi kuř řgens d teqbič u \add zi marra\add* ccuɛub d iřsawen. Nitni bedden zzat i řɛarc d yezmar, arḍen řeɛbayat tizirarin d ticemřařin, uca ɣarsen tiseḍwin n tini deg ifassen nsen,  
\v 10 ttřaɣan s jjehd:  
\b  
\m \qt “Asenjem aqa s AREBBI nneɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt wenni iqqimen x řɛarc\qt*  
\m \qt u s Yezmar.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Uca marra lmalakat tuɣa beddent nnḍent i řɛarc ak-d imɣaren d arebɛa n imuddaren, wḍan ɣar temmurt s wudmawen nsen qibač i řɛarc,  
\v 12 qqaren  
\b  
\m \qt “Amin!\qt*  
\m \qt Aɛuǧi d lbaraka\qt*  
\m \qt d tiɣit d uqadi\qt*  
\m \qt d ccan d ṣṣulṭa d jjehd\qt*  
\m \qt aqa-ten i AREBBI nneɣ\qt*  
\m \qt i řebda qaɛ.\qt*  
\m \qt Amin!”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Iṭṭef ijjen zeg imɣaren nni deg wawař, inna ayi: “Min ɛnan ina, inni yarḍen řeɛbayat ticemřařin, min ɛnan u manis dd-usin?”  
\v 14 Necc nniɣ as: “A sidi, cek i issnen.” Inna ayi: “Ina aqa usin-dd zi řmeḥnet tameqqrant. Aqa nitni sizdigen řeɛbayat nsen uca arrin tent d ticemřařin deg Idammen n Izmar.  
\v 15 S uyenni bedden nitni zzat i řɛarc n AREBBI uca sexxaren as ass d ǧiřet di Zzawect Tameqqrant, uca wenni iqqimen x řɛarc ad xasen iwwet \add Aqiḍun nnes\add*.  
\v 16 War iqqim ɛad ad ǧaẓen niɣ ad ffaden, war ten tᵉttqeddi uřa d tafuct uřa d ict n jjurret n řeḥmu, \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Ica. 49:10. \x*  
\v 17 minzi Izmar nni iǧan di řwesṭ n řɛarc ad ten yarwes, ad ten indeh ɣar Tudart u ɣar tařawin n waman, uca Netta ad asen imseḥ kuř ameṭṭa zi tiṭṭawin nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 7:17 \xt Ica. 25:8; Izhd. 23:1; Asa. 21:4. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Acemmiɛ wiss sebɛa  
\m
\v 1 Ařami yarzem Netta \bd acemmiɛ wiss sebɛa\bd*, tuɣa ajenna yarsa ɛřaḥař azyen n tsaɛɛet.   
\b  
\m
\v 2 Uca ẓriɣ \bd sebɛa n lmalakat\bd* nni ibedden zzat i AREBBI uca immewc asent \bd sebɛa n waccawen n uyicc n icarri\bd*.   
\b  
\m
\v 3 Aqa ijj n lmalak nneɣni yusa-dd, yuyur ad ibedd ɣar uɛalṭar s ict n teqduḥt n wureɣ i řebxur. Immewc as waṭṭas n řebxur ḥima ad t iwehheb ak-d tẓaǧitin n marra imqeddasen x uɛalṭar qibač i řɛarc.  
\v 4 Uca arriḥet n řebxur ak-d tẓaǧitin n imqeddasen tuɣa tᵉttgeɛɛad zeg ufus n lmalak ɣar zzat n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 8:4 \xt Izhd. 141:2. \x*  
\v 5 Lmalak iksi taqduḥt n řebxur, iccur i-tt s tmessi zeg uɛalṭar uca inḍar i-t ɣar temmurt uca usin-dd wajjajen d tmijjawin d wassamen d ijj n wenhezzi n temmurt.   
\b  
\m
\v 6 Uca ḥezzment sebɛa n lmalakat tinni ɣar iǧa \bd sebɛa n waccawen n uyicc n icarri\bd* ḥima ad \add daysen\add* suḍent.   
\m
\v 7 \bd Uca isuḍ umezwaru\bd* \add di řbuq nnes\add* uca tewḍa-dd tebruri d tmessi xeǧḍent ak-d waman, ttwamenḍarent x temmurt, uca tecmeḍ ict n ttuřut n temmurt d ict n ttuřut n tcejjura uřa d marra arbiɛ n temmurt icmeḍ.   
\m
\v 8 \bd Xenni isuḍ wenni d wiss tnayen\bd* \add di řbuq nnes\add* uca ca n tmesřact am wedrar ameqqran icemmḍen, immenḍar di řebḥar uca ict n ttuřut n řebḥar idweř d idammen, \x ◘ \xo 8:8 \xt Ica. 13:13, 19; Irm. 51:25\x*  
\v 9 u ict n ttuřut n imuddaren di řebḥar inni ɣarsen řeɛmar, mmuten, uca ict n ttuřut n iɣarruba tareddeǧ. \f ◼ \fr 8:9 \ft \+fk imuddaren\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘iwdan’ d ‘lḥayawanat’ d marra min iddaren nni izemmar ad yuyur.\f*   
\m
\v 10 \bd Xenni isuḍ wenni d wiss třata\bd* \add di řbuq nnes\add* uca iwḍa-dd ijj n itri ameqqran zeg ujenna, yurɣa am yijj n uɛeccař n tmessi, iwḍa-dd x ict n ttuřut n iɣezran u x tařawin n waman.  
\v 11 Itri-ya qqaren-as ‘Absinta’, \add niɣ ‘cciḥ’\add*. Uca ict n ttuřut n waman tedweř tarzeg am ‘absint’, uca mmuten aṭṭas n yewdan s waman umi dewřen d imerzagen.   
\m
\v 12 \bd Xenni isuḍ wenni d wiss arebɛa\bd* \add di řbuq nnes\add* uca tᵉttwaṭṭef ict n ttuřut n tfuct d ict n ttuřut n tziri d ict n ttuřut n itran, \add ařami\add* tbbarcen ict n ttuřut zzaysen, war tᵉttiři ɛad tfawt i yict n ttuřut n uziř uca ammu uřa di ǧiřet.   
\m
\v 13 Uca sřiɣ ijj n ugider iṭṭaw-dd di řwesṭ n ujenna, iqqar: “\bd Uct, uct, uct\bd* x yinni izeddɣen x temmurt x ssibbet n tmijjawin inneɣni n \bd waccawen n icarri\bd* n třata n lmalakat i ɣa isuḍen ɛad \add di řbuq\add*!”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\m
\v 1 \bd Xenni isuḍ wenni d wiss xemsa\bd* \add di řbuq nnes\add* uca ẓriɣ ijj n yetri iwḍa-dd zeg ujenna x temmurt, temmewc as tasarut n uqemmum n tesraft yuǧɣen. \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt Lk. 8:31; Asa. 17:8. \x*  
\v 2 Uca igeɛɛed-dd ddexxan zeg uqemmum n tesraft, am ddexxan n tefqunt tameqqrant iḥman, uca tfuct d řeɛwin bbarcnen s ddexxan n tesraft.  
\v 3 Zi ddexxan ffɣen-dd zzayes iburexsen ɣar temmurt, temmewc asen ṣṣulṭa am tenni iǧan ɣar tɣarḍmiwin n temmurt.  
\v 4 Ittwanna asen, maḥend war jeyyḥen arbiɛ n temmurt uřa d qaɛ aɣemmuy aziza uřa d ticejjura, mɣir iwdan waha inni war ɣar iǧi ucemmiɛ n AREBBI x tenyart nsen. \f ◼ \fr 9:4 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:4 \xt Ḥiz. 9:4; Yḥ. 6:26; Asa. 6:6; 7:2, 3. \x*  
\v 5 Temmewc asen \add tzemmar\add* maḥend war ten neqqen, maca ad ten ɛeddben řqedd n xemsa n iyuren, uca aɛeddeb nsen am uɛeddeb n tɣarḍent xmi tᵉtteqqes i bnadem.   
\m
\v 6 Deg wussan nni ad arzun iwdan x řmewt, \add maca\add* war tt ttᵉṭṭifen, uca ad ttaren ad mmten, \add maca\add* řmewt ad zzaysen tarweř. \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Ica. 2:19; Irm. 8:3; Ḥuc. 10:8; Lk. 23:30; Asa. 6:16. \x*  
\v 7 Iburexsen ggin am yiysan iwejden i umenɣi, u ɣarsen x izeǧifen nsen \add ca\add* am ttijan axmi tent ggin s wureɣ, u iɣembab nsen am iɣembab n iwdan, \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Uf. 10:4; Yuw. 2:4\x*  
\v 8 u acuwwaf nsen am ucuwwaf n temɣarin u tiɣmas nsen am tinni n wayraden, \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Yuw. 1:6\x*  
\v 9 u tuɣa ɣarsen tcappat x idmaren nsen am tcappat n wuzzař \add i useřqi\add*, u ddriz n wafriwen nsen am ddriz n ikarruten ak-d waṭṭas n iysan itteqnunnuyen ɣar umenɣi,  
\v 10 u ɣarsen ikennasen am yinni n tɣarḍmiwin u tuɣa din isennanen deg ikennasen nsen. Nitni ɣarsen ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad ssehwan druct x iwdan, řmijař n xemsa n iyuren.  
\v 11 Nitni ɣarsen lmalak n tesraft d ajeǧid xasen, qqaren as s Tɛibranit ‘Abaddu’ u s Tramit qqaren as ‘Cara’. \f ◼ \fr 9:11 \ft \+fk Abaddu\ft  - isem-a yusa-d zi tutlayt n tɛibranit uca ixs ad yini 'areyyeb' niɣ 'areddeǧ' (Asa. 9:11).\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 \bd Uct tamezwarut teɛdu\bd*, awarni man aya ad dd-asent ɛad tnayen n wuctat. \x ◘ \xo 9:12 \xt Asa. 8:13. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Awarni man aya \bd isuḍ lmalak wiss setta\bd* \add di řbuq nnes\add* uca sřiɣ tmijja i dd-yusin zi arebɛa n waccawen n uɛalṭar n wureɣ i ibedden qibač i AREBBI,  
\v 14 tenna i lmalak wiss setta i ɣar iǧa \bd uyicc n icarri\bd*: “Fsiy i arebɛa n lmalakat nni icarfen ṭṭarf n iɣzar ameqqran, Lfuraṭ.”  
\v 15 Uca arxun asen i arebɛa n lmalakat nni tuɣa iwejden dinni ɣar wass d uyur d useggʷas, ḥima ad nɣent ict n ttuřut n iwdan.  
\v 16 Tuɣa řqedd n řɛeskarat n yinni ineddhen iysan tyuya n ɛecra-ařaf s ɛecra n řuřuf, uca sřiɣ mecḥař di ǧan. \f ◼ \fr 9:16 \ft \+fk tyuya n ɛecra-ařaf s ɛecra n řuřuf\ft  - řqedd nsen ammu 2 x 10.000 x 10.000 ixs ad yini 200 milyun, ixs ad yini ijj n řɛeskar d ameqqran aṭṭas s waṭṭas.\f*  
\v 17 Ammu i ẓriɣ iysan di řewḥiy, aqa inni xasen inyin tuɣa ssdurruyen idmaren nsen s tcappat n wuzzař \add i useřqi d tizeggʷaɣin\add* am tmessi, cabent, d tiwraɣin am řecbareyyet. Izeǧifen n iysan nni am yizeǧifen n wayraden uca zeg iqemmumen nsen teffeɣ-dd zzaysen tmessi d ddexxan d řecbareyyet.  
\v 18 Aqa ict n ttuřut n iwdan tᵉttwaneɣ s třata-ya n jjrayeḥ: s tmessi d řecbareyyet d ddexxan i dd-itteffɣen zeg iqemmumen nsen.  
\v 19 Minzi ṣṣulṭa nsen aqa-tt deg iqemmumen d ikennasen nsen, \add minzi ikennasen nsen ggin am ifiɣran nni ɣar iǧa izeǧifen, uca ttjeyyḥen zzaysen iwdan\add*.   
\m
\v 20 Iwdan iqqimen, inni war ittwanɣen ca s jjrayeḥ-a, war tuben ca zi řxedmet n ifassen nsen ařami war ɛebbden ɛad ccwaṭen d l’aṣnam n wureɣ d nnuqart d nnḥas d weẓru d ukeccuḍ, inni war ittwiřin, war ittesřin, war igguren, \x ◘ \xo 9:20 \xt Izhd. 115:4, 5, 6, 7; 135:15. \x*  
\v 21 uca nitni war tuben ca zeg wenɣay nsen, řa zi tseḥḥart nsen uřa zi farq-ccɣeř nsen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Lmalak ɣares wedlis ameẓyan  
\m
\v 1 Uca ẓriɣ ijj n lmalak nneɣni ihwa-dd zeg ujenna, tuɣa yarḍ aseynu uca tasřit n wenẓar n ujenna tbedd as x uzeǧif. Aɣembub nnes igga am tfuct, iḍaren nnes am ipilaren n tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt Mt. 17:2; Asa. 1:15. \x*  
\v 2 Iṭṭef deg ufus nnes ijj n wedlis \add ittwannḍen\add* ameẓyan yarzem. Issars aḍar nnes afusi x řebḥar, aḍar nnes azeřmaḍ x temmurt,  
\v 3 uca iřaɣa s tmijja tejhed, am wayrad ittzehharen, uca awarni řami dd-iřaɣa, jjin sebɛa n wajjajen ad sřen tmijjawin nsen.  
\v 4 Řami kemmřen sebɛa n wajjajen nni awař nsen, tuɣa xseɣ ad t ariɣ, \add maca\add* sřiɣ i yict n \bd tmijja třaɣa-dd zeg ujenna wiss sebɛa\bd*: “Egg acemmiɛ x min nnan sebɛa n wajjajen, war t ttari ca.” \x ◘ \xo 10:4 \xt Dan. 8:26; 12:4; 2 Kur. 12:2\x*   
\m
\v 5 Lmalak nni tuɣa ẓriɣ ibedd x řebḥar d temmurt, iksi afus nnes ɣar ujenna \x ◘ \xo 10:5 \xt Dan. 12:7. \x*  
\v 6 uca ijjuǧ ɣar wenni iddaren i řebda qaɛ, wenni iggin ajenna d min dayes u tammurt d min dayes uřa d řebḥar d min dayes:  
\b  
\m \bd “War teqqim bu řweqt \+bdit ɛad\+bdit*!”\bd* \x ◘ \xo 10:6 \xt Asa. 11:15. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 Maɣar deg wussan n lmalak wiss sebɛa, xmi ɣa isuḍ netta \add di řbuq nnes\add*, ggur ad ikmeř ssirr n AREBBI nni tuɣa ittbarreḥ i imsexxaren nnes, inabiyyen.  
\v 8 Uca tmijja zeg ujenna i sřiɣ tessiweř ɣari ict n twařa nneɣnit, tenna: “Uyur, ksi adlis \add ittwannḍen\add* ameẓyan yarezmen i iǧan deg ufus n lmalak nni ibedden x řebḥar d temmurt.”  
\v 9 Uca uyureɣ ɣar lmalak, ttareɣ as ad ayi iwc adlis \add ittwannḍen\add* ameẓyan. Inna ayi: “Ksi \add adlis-a ameẓyan\add*, teccid t uca ad issarzeg aɛeddis nnec, maca deg uqemmum nnec ad yiři \add d amiẓid\add* am tamment.” \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt Ḥiz. 2:9-3:1-4\x*  
\v 10 Necc ksiɣ adlis ameẓyan \add ittwannḍen\add* zeg ufus n lmalak uca cciɣ t. Tuɣa-t d amiẓid deg uqemmum inu, \add maca\add* řami t cciɣ, yarzeg deg uɛeddis inu.  
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi: “Temmewc as ɛawed řweqt maḥend ad tnebbid i waṭṭas n řegnus d temmura d iřsawen d ijeǧiden.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Tnayen n řechud  
\m
\v 1 Uca immewc ayi ijj n uɣanim, igga am yijj n uqeṭṭab \add n řeɛbar\add*, uca ibedd \add din\add* lmalak, inna: “Kkar uca ɛbar Zzawect Tameqqrant n AREBBI d uɛalṭar d yinni dayes iɛebbden, \f ◼ \fr 11:1 \ft \+fk dayes\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘di Zzawect Tameqqrant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt Ḥiz. 40:3-49; 41; 42; 43. \x*  
\v 2 \add maca\add* řemraḥ nni ɣar daxeř n Zzawect Tameqqrant, ejj i-t, war t ttɛebbar, minzi aqa immewc i řegnus uca nitni ad ɛefsen x tendint iqeddsen \bd tnayen u arebɛin n iyuren\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 11:2 \ft \+fk ad ɛefsen\ft  - niɣ: ‘ad ɛejnen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:2 \xt Asa. 13:5. \x*  
\v 3 Necc ad wceɣ ṣṣulṭa i tnayen n řechud inu, maḥend ad nebban \add s wawař n Arebbi\add* \bd ařef u mitayen u-settin n wussan\bd*, am yarḍen txancet n wecḍan.”   
\m
\v 4 Nitni d tnayen n tzitunin d tnayen n řeqnadeř i ibedden zzat i wudem n Sidi n marra tammurt. \x ◘ \xo 11:4 \xt Zak. 4:3, 14. \x*  
\v 5 Mařa din ca n yijjen ixs ad ten ihweř, ad teffeɣ tmessi zeg uqemmum nsen uca ad tecc řɛedyan nsen. Ammu i ɣa ttwanɣen inni ixsen ad ten ḍarren.  
\v 6 Nitni ɣarsen ṣṣulṭa maḥend ad qqnen ajenna, ḥima war dd-iweṭṭi wenẓar deg wussan nni di ɣa nebban nitni, u ɣarsen ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad arren aman d idammen u ḥima ad seyyḥen tammurt s marra jjriḥect meřmi ma xsen. \x ◘ \xo 11:6 \xt Uf. 7; 8; 9; 10; 12; 1 Ij. 17:1. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Xmi ɣa kemmřen cchadat nsen, ad dd-igeɛɛed řweḥc zi řaǧaɣ, ad kisen immneɣ, ad xasen iɣelleb uca ad ten ineɣ. \x ◘ \xo 11:7 \xt Dan. 7:21; Asa. 13:7, 11. \x*  
\v 8 Řxecbat nsen \add ad iřint\add* deg wazzay n tendint tameqqrant umi qqaren s řmeɛna arruḥi nnes ‘Sadum’ d ‘Miṣra’, mani nɣin Siditsen x ṣṣalib. \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Irm. 23:14; Asa. 7:2, 5; 18:10. \x*  
\v 9 Uca zi ccuɛub d tqebbař d iřsawen d řegnus ad ẓaren \add iwdan\add* řxecbat nsen, \add řqedd n\add* třata n wussan d wezyen, war ttejjin řxecbat nsen ad ttwammarsent deg imeḍřan.  
\v 10 Imezdaɣ n temmurt ad zzaysen farḥen, ad ɛeyyden, ad arezfen ijjen ɣar wenneɣni, ad ssekken ikaduten i wayawya, minzi tnayen n inabiyyen-a tuɣa ɣezzan deg imezdaɣ n temmurt.   
\m
\v 11 \add Maca\add* awarni třata n wussan d wezyen yudef daysen Arruḥ Iddaren zi AREBBI uca kkaren, bedden x iḍaren nsen u tewḍa-dd xasen Arruḥ n Tudart uca tiggʷudi temɣar tewḍa-dd x \add marra\add* inni ten iẓrin. \x ◘ \xo 11:11 \xt Ḥiz. 37:5, 10\x*  
\v 12 Nitni sřin ict n tmijja tejhed \add tᵉttřaɣa\add* zeg ujenna, teqqar asen: “Geɛɛdem-dd da!” Uca nitni geɛɛden ɣar ujenna deg useynu uca řɛedyan nsen ẓrin ten.   
\m
\v 13 Di tsaɛɛet nni imsar ijj n wenhezzi n temmurt d ameqqran. Ict n tɛeccart n tendint tehdem uca sebɛa-ařaf n yeryazen ɣarsen isem \add icennɛen\add* mmuten s wenhezzi-ya n temmurt. Wi iqqimen, dewřen ggʷeden aṭṭas uca ssuɛřan zi AREBBI n ujenna.   
\m
\v 14 \bd ‘Xzar, tnayen n wuctat ɛdunt, uca xzar ‘Uct!’ wiss třata ad dd-tas deɣya.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 11:14 \xt Asa. 8:13; 9:12; 15:1. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 \bd Lmalak wiss sebɛa isuḍ\bd* \add di řbuq nnes\add* uca kkarent-i-dd tmijjawin timeqqranin deg ujenna, ttřaɣant:  
\b  
\m \qt “Tagelda n ddunect aqa-tt n AREBBI nneɣ u n Lmasiḥ nnes, uca Netta ad iḥkem am Ujeǧid i řebda qaɛ.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Arebɛa u ɛicrin n imɣaren, inni iqqimen zzat i AREBBI x řekrasi nsen igellden, wḍan s uɣembub nsen \add ɣar temmurt\add* uca sejden i AREBBI,  
\v 17 nnan:  
\b  
\m \qt “Neccin nettqada Cek, a SIDI AREBBI,\qt*  
\m \qt Amzemmar x kuřci,\qt*  
\m \qt Cek d wenni iǧan d wenni tuɣa,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa teksid jjehd nnec ameqqran\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl deg ufus nnec,\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt uca tebdid ad tḥekmed am Ujeǧid.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt Asa. 1:4, 8; 4:18; 16:5. \x*   
\m
\v 18 \qt Řegnus tuɣa xeyyqen \+tl xak,\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maca\+tl* yusa-dd weɣḍab nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt uca tiweḍ-dd řweqt n imettinen\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad ttwaḥasben\qt*  
\m \qt u ḥima ad temmewc řmunet\qt*  
\m \qt i imsexxaren nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt inabiyyen, u i imqeddasen\qt*  
\m \qt u i yinni itteggʷeden Isem nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt am imeẓyanen am yimeqqranen,\qt*  
\m \qt u Cek ad tareyybed\qt*  
\m \qt inni ittaredǧen tammurt.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Tᵉnnurzem Zzawect Tameqqrant deg ujenna ařami tᵉttwaẓar Ttabut n Řɛahd nnes di Zzawect Tameqqrant, uca kkaren wassamen d wajjajen d tmijjawin uca imsar ijj n wenhezzi n temmurt u \add wḍan\add* \add ibquqen\add* imeqqranen \add n\add* tebruri. \f ◼ \fr 11:19 \ft \+fk Ttabut\ft  - netta d ijj n ssenduq n ukeccuḍ n ukasiya iɣeǧfen s wureɣ. Tuɣa dayes tnayen n teřwiḥin n weẓru n Ccariɛa d taɣɣarct n Harun nni ittwannuwcen d ij n uzenbiř dayes ‘manna’. Xzar Ɛib. 9:4.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:19 \xt Asa. 15:5. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Tamɣart d řhaycet  
\m
\v 1 Xenni tᵉttwaẓar \bd ict n řeɛřamet tameqqrant deg ujenna\bd*: \bd ict n tmeṭṭut\bd* tyarḍ tafuct, u taziri sadu iḍaren nnes uca ɣares x uzeǧif nnes ijj n ttaj s tenɛac n itran.  
\v 2 Tuɣa teksi ddeyset, tesɣuyyu s řewjeɛ, tᵉttwaḥṣar s unezbar n tarut.   
\m
\v 3 Xenni tᵉttwaẓar \bd ict n řeɛřamet nneɣni deg ujenna\bd*, aqa din \bd ict n řhaycet tameqqrant tazeggwaɣt am tmessi\bd*, ɣares sebɛa n izeǧifen d ɛecra n waccawen, uca x izeǧifen nnes sebɛa n ttijan. \f ◼ \fr 12:3 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - nitni d iqaccawen n lḥayawan.\f*  
\v 4 uca akennas nnes ifarḍ ict n ttuřut n itran zeg ujenna, tessẓareyyeḍ i-ten ɣar temmurt. Uca řhaycet tuɣa tbedd zzat i tmeṭṭut i ɣa yarwen, ḥima ad tṣarḍ Mmis xmi t-i-dd i ɣa taruw.  
\v 5 Uca turuw-dd Mmis, Aryaz nni i ɣa iḥekmen x marra řegnus s uzeǧaḍ n wuzzař, uca Mmis immeksi deɣya ɣar AREBBI u ɣar řɛarc nnes. \x ◘ \xo 12:5 \xt Izhd. 2:9; Asa. 2:27. \x*  
\v 6 Maca tameṭṭut tarweř ɣar řexřa, ɣar mani tuɣa d as igga AREBBI amcan ḥima ad as sseccen, \bd řqedd n wařef u-mitayn u-settin n wussan\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 12:6 \xt Izhd. 55:7-19; Asa. 11:3. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Uca ikkar \bd umenɣi deg ujenna\bd*. Mixayil d lmalakat nnes mmenɣent ak-d řhaycet, uca uřa d řhaycet d lmalakat nnes mmenɣent,  
\v 8 maca nitni war jhiden ca uca war ittwif ɛad wemcan deg ujenna i nitni. \x ◘ \xo 12:8 \xt Dan. 2:35. \x*  
\v 9 \bd Temmenḍar-dd řhaycet tameqqrant\bd*, nettat d ufiɣar nni tuɣa zic, qqaren as ‘ibřis’ niɣ ‘cciṭan’, wenni iɣekkwan marra tammurt, \add wah\add*, aqa immenḍar-dd x temmurt uca lmalakat nnes mmenḍarent-i-dd \add ɛawed\add* akides. \x ◘ \xo 12:9 \xt Lk. 10:18; Asa. 20:2. \x*  
\v 10 Uca sřiɣ ict n tmijja tameqqrant zeg ujenna teqqar s jjehd:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa \+tl yusa-dd\+tl* ufekki d ṣṣulṭa\qt*  
\m \qt d Tgeldit n AREBBI nneɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi wenni iḍeřmen aytmatneɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa immenḍar,\qt*  
\m \qt wenni i ten iḍeřmen ass d ǧiřet.\qt*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Ɣellben \+tl xas\+tl* s Idammen n Izmar,\qt*  
\m \qt d wawař n cchadet nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt uca nitni war ssɛizzen ca tudart nsen\qt*  
\m \qt ař řmewt.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt X uyenni, farḥem, \+tl a\+tl* ijenwan\qt*  
\m \qt d yinni daysen izeddɣen!\qt*  
\m \bdit Uct\bdit* \qt x temmurt d řebḥar,\qt*  
\m \qt ibřis aqa ihwa-dd ɣarwem\qt*  
\m \qt s tefqeḥt nnes imɣaren aṭṭas,\qt*  
\m \qt issen ad ɣares iqqim\qt*  
\m \qt drust n řweqt waha.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 12:12 \xt Izhd. 96:11; Ica. 49:13; Asa. 8:13. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Ařami řhaycet tufa ixef nnes temmenḍar ɣar temmurt, teḍfar tameṭṭut i dd-yurwen \add Mmis\add* d Awtem.  
\v 14 Mmewcen as i tmeṭṭut tnayen n wefriwen n ugider ameqqran, ḥima ad teḍwu ɣar wemcan nnes di řexřa, maḥend ad tᵉttwassecc dinni, \bd ijj n řmijař n řweqt d řewqat d ijj n wezyen \+bdit n yijj n řmijař n řweqt\+bdit*\bd*, mani war tt iẓarr ufiɣar. \f ◼ \fr 12:14 \ft \+fk ijj n řmijař n řweqt d řewqat d ijj n wezyen \+bdit n yijj n řmijař n řweqt\+bdit*\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini ‘ijj n useggʷas d tnayen n iseggʷusa d wezyen n useggʷas’. Xzar Asa. 12:6.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt Asa. 2:6. \x*  
\v 15 Afiɣar issusef zeg uqemmum nnes awarni i tmeṭṭut, igga ict n řḥemřet n waman am yeɣzar, ḥima ad tt awyen waman.  
\v 16 Tammurt tɛawen tameṭṭut uca tarzem temmurt aqemmum nnes, teḥruw iɣzar wenni dd-issusfen řhaycet zeg uqemmum nnes.  
\v 17 Uca řhaycet txeyyeq aṭṭas x tmeṭṭut uca tuyur ḥima ad temmneɣ ak-d yinni iqqimen zi zzariɛet nnes uca ak-d inni itteṭṭfen di tweṣṣa n AREBBI u di cchadet n Yasuɛ. \f ◼ \fr 12:17 \ft \+fk zzariɛet nnes\ft  - ixs ad yini Lmasiḥ (xzar Amz. 3:15) u yenni iqqimen aqa-ten d řmuminin inni yumnen di Lmasiḥ.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Řweḥc zi řebḥar u řweḥc zi temmurt  
\m
\v 1 Uca dewřeɣ beddeɣ x ijdi \add ɣar tma\add* n řebḥar, uca ẓriɣ \bd ijj n řweḥc igeɛɛed-dd zi řebḥar\bd*, ɣares ɛecra n waccawen d sebɛa n izeǧifen. X waccawen nnes ɛecra n ttijan uca x izeǧifen nnes ittwari xasen ijj n yisem n ttekfir. \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt Dan. 7:20; Asa. 17:3. \x*  
\v 2 Řweḥc i ẓriɣ, yarwes deg uɣiřas, iḍaren nnes am yiḍaren n ddub, axenfuc nnes am uxenfuc n wayrad. Řhaycet tewca as jjehd nnes d řɛarc nnes uřa d ṣṣulṭa imɣaren.  
\v 3 Ijjen zeg izeǧifen nnes igga axmi t wtin ař řmewt, xenni ittwassgenfa uyezzim nnes i iggin axmi iyzem ař řmewt, uca marra tammurt teḍfar řweḥc s utebhet ameqqran.  
\v 4 Aqa nitni ɛebden řhaycet, minzi nettat tewca ṣṣulṭa i řweḥc, uca nitni ɛebden řweḥc, nnan: “Wi yarwesen di řweḥc?” u: “Wi izemmaren ad kides immɛařan?” \x ◘ \xo 13:4 \xt Asa. 18:18. \x*  
\v 5 Immewc as \add i řweḥc\add* aqemmum nni issawařen s ukebbar u s uceqqef \add di AREBBI\add*, uca temmewc as ṣṣulṭa ḥima ad ixdem \bd \+bdit i yijj n řqedd n\+bdit* tnayen u-rebɛin n iyuren\bd*. \f ◼ \fr 13:5 \ft \+fk tnayen u-rebɛin n iyuren\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini 1260 n wussan niɣ 3½ n iseggʷusa (xzar Asa. 12:6, 14).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:5 \xt Ayub 15:25; Asa. 11:2. \x*  
\v 6 Uca netta yarzem aqemmum nnes ḥima ad iceqqef di AREBBI, u ḥima ad iceqqef deg Yisem nnes u di Tzeddiɣt n yinni izeddɣen deg ujenna.  
\v 7 Immewc as ṣṣulṭa maḥend ad immneɣ ak-d imqeddasen u maḥend ad xasen iɣelleb. Temmewc as ṣṣulṭa x marra tiqebbař d ccuɛub d yiřsawen d řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 13:7 \xt Dan. 7:21; Asa. 11:7. \x*  
\v 8 Marra inni tuɣa izeddɣen di temmurt ad t ɛebden, inni umi war ittwazemmemen \add ismawen nsen\add* deg Wedlis ittwanḍen n Tudart n Yezmar wenni umi ittwaɣarṣ qbeř tamarsiwt n ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 13:8 \xt Uf. 32:33; Fil. 4:3; Asa. 3:5; 17:8; 20:12; 21:27; Asa. 21:27. \x*  
\v 9 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen, ejj i-t ad iseř.   
\m
\v 10 Mařa \add din\add* ijjen wenni issidfen ɣar tmeḥbast, ad ittwandeh netta \add s yixef nnes\add* ɣar tmeḥbast. Inni inɣin s ssif, ad ttwanɣen s ssif: aqa da \add ittban-dd\add* l’iman d ṣṣbar n imqeddasen. \x ◘ \xo 13:10 \xt Amz. 9:6; Irm. 43:11; Mt. 26:52; Asa. 14:12. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* ẓriɣ \bd ijj n řweḥc nneɣni ittgeɛɛad-dd zi temmurt.\bd* Tuɣa ɣares tnayen n waccawen uca yarwes deg Izmar, \add maca\add* issiweř am řhaycet. \x ◘ \xo 13:11 \xt Asa. 11:7. \x*  
\v 12 Tuɣa iḥekkem s marra ṣṣulṭa n řweḥc amezwaru zzates, yarra-dd tammurt d imezdaɣ nnes marra ad ɛebden řweḥc amezwaru, wenni iggenfan zeg uyezzim i iggin axmi iyzem ař řmewt. \x ◘ \xo 13:12 \xt Asa. 19:20. \x*  
\v 13 Netta ad igg řeɛřamat timeqqranin ařami i ɣa yarr timessi ad dd-tehwa zeg ujenna x temmurt qibač i \add tiṭṭawin n\add* iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 13:13 \xt 2 Ts. 2:9; Asa. 16:14. \x*  
\v 14 Ad iɣwa inni izeddɣen di temmurt s řeɛřamat i d as immewcen ḥima ad tent igg qibač i \add tiṭṭawin n\add* řweḥc \add amezwaru\add*, maḥend ad yini i yinni izeddɣen di temmurt ad kkaren ad ssbedden ijj n řexyař i řweḥc, wenni tuɣa iyzem s ssif, \add maca\add* iddar \add ɛad\add*. \x ◘ \xo 13:14 \xt Aɛwd. 13:2; Mt. 24:24; Asa. 16:14; 19:20. \x*  
\v 15 Uca immewc as ad igg ijj n arruḥ i řexyař n řweḥc u ḥima ad igg belli marra inni war iɛebbden řweḥc, ad ttwanɣen. \x ◘ \xo 13:15 \xt Asa. 19:20. \x*  
\v 16 Uca ad igg maḥend ad temmewc i marra, i imeẓyanen d imeqqranen, i aytbab n wagřa d imezřaḍ, i ayt n ccan d isemɣan, ict n řmarka x ufus nsen afusi niɣ x tenyart nsen, \f ◼ \fr 13:16 \ft \+fk tanyart\ft  - niɣ: ‘tawarna’.\f*  
\v 17 maḥend uřa d ijj war izemmar ad iseɣ niɣ ad izzenz mɣir wenni x teǧa řmarka n yisem n řweḥc niɣ nnumru n yisem nnes. \x ◘ \xo 13:17 \xt Asa. 14:11. \x*   
\m
\v 18 Danita teǧa tiɣit: wenni ɣar iǧa řeɛqeř, ejj i-t ad iḥseb nnumru n řweḥc, minzi netta d nnumru n ijj n bnadem uca nnumru nnes d setta-mya u-setta u-settin. \x ◘ \xo 13:18 \xt 1 Ij. 10:14; 2 Im. 9:13; Ɛiz. 2:13; Asa. 17:9. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Izmar x wedrar n Ṣihyun  
\m
\v 1 Uca ẓriɣ, aqa Izmar ibedd-dd x wedrar n Ṣihyun, uca akides mya u-arebɛa u-rebɛin-ařef, inni x tenyart nsen yura Isem nnes d Yisem n Babas. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt 2 Im. 23:7; Ica. 31:4; Izhd. 2:6; Asa. 7:4\x*   
\m
\v 2 Sřiɣ ict n tmijja tusa-dd zeg ujenna, am řḥess n waṭṭas n waman u am řḥess n wajjaj ameqqran, uca řḥess i sřiɣ tuɣa am yijj n bu-lharpa ittiraren di lharpa nnes. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Yuw. 4:8; Asa. 1:15; 5:8; 10:3\x*  
\v 3 Aqa nitni ɣennjen \add min iǧan\add* am yijj n yezři n uṣebbeḥ d jdid \add qaɛ\add* zzat i řɛarc u zzat i arebɛa n imuddaren d imɣaren, uca uřa d ijj war izemmar ad iřmed izři \add aya\add* n uṣebbeḥ mɣir mya u-arebɛa u-rebɛin-ařef, inni ittwafdin zi temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 14:3 \xt Asa. 5:9. \x*  
\v 4 Ina d inni war issefseden ixef nsen ak-d temɣarin, minzi nitni d iɛezriyyen imezdagen. Nitni ḍeffaren Izmar mani ma ikka. Aqa ina ittwafdin zeg iwdan \add am\add* \add ṣṣabet\add* tamezwarut i AREBBI u i Yezmar. \x ◘ \xo 14:4 \xt 2 Kur. 11:2. \x*  
\v 5 Aqa war ittwiffi ca řɣecc deg uqemmum nsen, aqa war daysen bu řɛib. \x ◘ \xo 14:5 \xt Ṣaf. 3:13; Afa. 5:27. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Třata n lmalakat  
\m
\v 6 Uca ẓriɣ \bd ijj n lmalak nneɣni\bd* tuɣa iṭṭaw di řwesṭ n ujenna, ɣares Řexbar Aṣebḥan i Řebda ḥima ad zzayes ibarreḥ i yinni izeddɣen di temmurt, i kuř řgens d cceɛb d teqbič d yiřes,  
\v 7 uca inna s jjehd:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ggʷedem AREBBI, wcem as-dd aɛuǧi,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa tasaɛɛet n lḥisab nnes tiweḍ-dd.\qt*  
\m \qt Sejdem i wenni iggin ajenna d temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt d řebḥar d tařawin n waman.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:7 \xt Amz. 1:1; Izhd. 33:6; 124:8; 146:6; Řex. 14:15; 17:24. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Uca \bd wenneɣni, wenni d wiss tnayen\bd*, iḍfar i-t, inna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa tewḍa, aqa tewḍa \+tl tendint\+tl* tameqqrant Babil,\qt*  
\m \qt i yejjin ad swen marra řegnus \+tl zi binu\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt n tefqeḥt n farq-ccɣeř nnes.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:8 \xt Ica. 21:9; Irm. 51:8; Asa. 16:19; 17:5; 18:2, 10, 21. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Uca \bd wenneɣni, ijj n lmalak wiss třata\bd*, iḍfar i-ten uca iřaɣa s jjehd:  
\b  
\m \qt “Wenni iɛebden řweḥc d řexyař nnes\qt*  
\m \qt d wenni iksin řmarka x tenyart nnes\qt*  
\m \qt niɣ deg ufus nnes,\qt*   
\m
\v 10 \qt d netta ad isu ɛawed\qt*  
\m \qt zi binu n tefqeḥt n SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt wenni isswejden břa axeǧeḍ\qt*  
\m \qt di řkas n weɣḍab nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ittwaɛeddeb\qt*  
\m \qt s tmessi d řecbareyyet\qt*  
\m \qt qibač i \+tl tiṭṭawin n\+tl* lmalakat iqeddsen\qt*  
\m \qt u qibač i \+tl tiṭṭawin n\+tl* Yezmar.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:10 \xt Asa. 16:19; 18;6; 19:20. \x*   
\m
\v 11 \qt Uca ddexxan n uɛeddeb nsen\qt*  
\m \qt ad iqqim igeɛɛed i řebda qaɛ.\qt*  
\m \qt War din bu arraḥet ass d ǧiřet\qt*  
\m \qt i wenni isejjden i řweḥc d řexyař nnes\qt*  
\m \qt u i wenni iksin řmarka n yisem nnes.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:11 \xt Asa. 19:3. \x*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Aqa da \+tl ittban-dd\+tl* ṣṣbar n imqeddasen,\qt*  
\m \qt inni itteṭṭfen di tweṣṣa n AREBBI\qt*  
\m \qt u ḥeṭṭan l’iman n Yasuɛ.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:12 \xt Asa. 13:10. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Uca sřiɣ ict n tmijja tᵉttřaɣa-dd zeg ujenna, teqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ari:\qt* \bdit Sseɛd\bdit* \qt n imettinen\qt*  
\m \qt inni i ɣa mmten di Siditneɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt zi řexxu tsawent!”\qt*  
\b  
\m \qt “Wah, inna Arruḥ, maɣar ad areyyḥen\qt*  
\m \qt zi řexdayem nsen!”,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl aqa řexdayem nsen ad ten ḍfarent.\+tl*\qt*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tameyra n temmurt  
\m
\v 14 Uca ẓriɣ, aqa \bd ijj n useynu d acemřař\bd*, uca x useynu iqqim xas wenni yarwesen deg ijj n \bd Mmis n bnadem\bd*, ɣares ttaj n wureɣ x uzeǧif nnes u amjar iqḍeɛ deg ufus nnes. \x ◘ \xo 14:14 \xt Ḥiz. 1:26; Dan. 7:13; Asa. 1:13. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 Uca \bd ijj n lmalak nneɣni\bd* iffeɣ-dd zi Zzawect Tameqqrant uca iřaɣa s jjehd x wenni iqqimen x useynu:  
\b  
\m \qt “Sekk-dd amjar nnec, mjar!\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa tasaɛɛet n tmeyra tiweḍ-dd!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:15 \xt Yuw. 4:13; Mt. 13:39. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Uca Wenni iqqimen x useynu, issekk-dd amjar nnes ɣar temmurt uca tᵉttwamjar temmurt.   
\m
\v 17 Uca \bd ijj n lmalak nneɣni\bd* iffeɣ-dd zi Zzawect Tameqqrant i iǧan deg ujenna, \add uca uřa d\add* netta ɣares ijj n wemjar iqḍeɛ.  
\v 18 Uca \bd ijj n lmalak nneɣni\bd* wenni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa x tmessi, iffeɣ-dd zeg uɛalṭar, uca iřaɣa-dd s jjehd x wenni ɣar iǧa wemjar iqḍeɛ, inna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Sekk-dd amjar nnec iqeḍɛen,\qt*  
\m \qt řqeḍ izekkunen n tzayarin n temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi aḍiř nnes aqa yiweḍ.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Uca lmalak issekk-dd amjar nnes ɣar temmurt, iřqeḍ aḍiř n tzayart n temmurt, inḍar i-t di tsirt tameqqrant n weɣḍab n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 14:19 \xt Asa. 19:15. \x*  
\v 20 Ḥaryen di tsirt n uḍiř ař barra n tendint uca ruccen-dd idammen zi tsirt ařami iwḍen ɣar sřimat n yeysan, řqedd n ařef u-mitayen n ‘istadiyyen’, \add ixs ad yini ɛřaḥař mitayen u-ɛicrin kilumitr\add*. \f ◼ \fr 14:20 \ft \+fk istadiyyen\ft  
\fp  ijj n řmeřɛeb di řweqt n Iyunaniyyen tuɣa ɣares ict tuzzugart n 185 mitr, ixs ad yini ‘inn n ustadiy’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 14:20 \xt Ica. 63:3. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Iẓři n inni iɣellben  
\m
\v 1 Uca \bd ẓriɣ\bd* deg ujenna ict n řeɛřamet nneɣni, d tameqqrant d tanebhet: \bd sebɛa n lmalakat nni dd-iwyen sebɛa n jjrayeḥ tineggura\bd*, minzi ikmeř zzaysent weɣḍab n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt Izhd. 7:12; Asa. 11:14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 2 Uca ẓriɣ ca ittemcabeh di řebḥar n zzaj, wenni ixeǧḍen ak-d tmessi, uca inni iɣellben x řweḥc d řexyař nnes d nnumru n yisem nnes, bedden x řebḥar n zzaj, ɣarsen lharpat n AREBBI.\x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Asa. 4:6; Mixa 7:18. \x*  
\v 3 Nitni ɣennjen izři n uṣebbeḥ n Musa, amsexxar n AREBBI, d yezři n uṣebbeḥ n Yezmar, qqaren:  
\b  
\m \qt “D timeqqranin d tṣebḥanin řexdayem nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a,\+tl* SIDI AREBBI, Amzemmar x kuřci,\qt*  
\m \qt řexdayem nnec d tasegda d tidett,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl a\+tl* Ajeǧid n n zzmanat!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:3 \xt Uf. 15:1-21; Aɛwd. 32:1-44; Izhd. 111:2; 139:14; 145:17. \x*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Man wen war Cek itteggʷeden, \+tl a\+tl* SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt man wen war issemɣaran Isem nnec?\qt*  
\m \qt Cek weḥḥdek i iǧan d amezdag qaɛ,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar marra řegnus ad dd-asen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad sejden zzatek,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi Cek tbaned d amsegged\qt*  
\m \qt di řeḥkamat nnec.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:4 \xt Irm. 10:6, 7; Zak. 14:16-20 \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 Awarni as ẓriɣ, aqa tennurzem Zzawect Tameqqrant n Tzeddiɣt n Cchadet deg ujenna, \x ◘ \xo 15:5 \xt Asa. 11:19. \x*  
\v 6 uca sebɛa n lmalakat nni ɣar ǧant sebɛa n jjrayeḥ ffɣent-i-dd zi Zzawect Tameqqrant, yarḍent řeqṭen azdad izdigen ittissiqen, uca ɣarsen x idmaren ijj n webyas n wureɣ. \x ◘ \xo 15:6 \xt Asa. 1:13. \x*  
\v 7 Uca ijjen zi arebɛa n imuddaren iwca asen i sebɛa n lmalakat \bd sebɛa n ṭṭawyat\bd*, ccurent s weɣḍab n AREBBI, wenni d Tudart i řebda qaɛ. “Amin!”  
\v 8 Uca tᵉttwaɛemmar Zzawect Tameqqrant s ddexxan \add i dd-itteffɣen\add* zeg uɛuǧi n AREBBI u zi jjehd nnes. Uřa d ijjen war izemmar ad dd-yadef ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant ař ɣa kkent qaɛ sebɛa n jjrayeḥ tinni dd-iwyen sebɛa n lmalakat. \x ◘ \xo 15:8 \xt Uf. 40:34; 1 Ij. 8:10; 2 Im. 5:14; Ica. 6:4. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Sebɛa n lmalakat s sebɛa n ṭṭawyat  
\m
\v 1 Uca \bd sřiɣ\bd* ict n tmijja zi Zzawect Tameqqrant tᵉttřaɣa x sebɛa n lmalakat nni, tenna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Uyurent, ttfarrɣent sebɛa n ṭṭawyat n weɣḍab n AREBBI x temmurt!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 16:1 \xt Ica. 66:6\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 2 Wenni d \bd amezwaru\bd* yuyur, ifarreɣ ṭṭawya nnes x temmurt. Uca idweř ijj n ubuɛrus d aɛeffan iqbeḥ ɣar iwdan i ɣar teǧa řmarka n řweḥc, inni isejden i řexyař nnes. \f ◼ \fr 16:2 \ft \+fk řexyař\ft  - niɣ ‘timtal’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 16:2 \xt Uf. 9:9, 10, 11; 1 Ṣm. 5:9; Asa. 13:14, 16, 17. \x*   
\m
\v 3 Xenni ifarreɣ \bd lmalak wiss tnayen\bd* ṭṭawya nnes di řebḥar uca idweř řebḥar am \add idammen n ijj n\add* umettin, uca kuř řeɛmar iddaren di řebḥar immut. \x ◘ \xo 16:3 \xt Uf. 7:17, 18, 20\x*   
\m
\v 4 Xenni ifarreɣ \bd lmalak wiss třata\bd* ṭṭawya nnes x iɣezran d tařawin, uca aman nsen dewřen d idammen.   
\b  
\m
\v 5 Uca sřiɣ i lmalak n waman iqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “Cek d amseggad,\qt*  
\m \qt Cek d wenni iǧan d wenni tuɣa,\qt*  
\m \qt d wenni d amezdag qaɛ,\qt*  
\m \qt umi tkemmřed řeḥkamat-a ammu.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 16:5 \xt Asa. 1:4, 8; 4:8; 11:17. \x*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Minzi nitni ssizzřen idammen\qt*  
\m \qt n inabiyyen d imqeddasen,\qt*  
\m \qt tewcid asen \+add ɛawed\+add* ad swen idammen,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar ammu i d asen dd-iffeɣ.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 16:6 \xt Mt. 23:34. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 Uca sřiɣ aqa aɛalṭar iqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “Wah, a SIDI AREBBI, Amzemmar x kuřci,\qt*  
\m \qt řeḥkamat nnec d tidett d tasegda.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 16:7 \xt Asa. 15:3. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Xenni ifarreɣ \bd lmalak wiss arebɛa\bd* ṭṭawya nnes x tfuct uca temmewc as \add i tfuct\add*, ḥima ad tecnef iwdan s tmessi.  
\v 9 Uca cemḍen iwdan s řɛabuq imɣaren n tmessi uca ceqqfen deg Yisem n AREBBI wenni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa x jjrayeḥ-a uca war tuben ca maḥend ad as wcin aɛuǧi. \x ◘ \xo 16:9 \xt Asa. 16:11, 21. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Xenni ifarreɣ \bd lmalak wiss xemsa\bd* ṭawya nnes x řɛarc n řweḥc uca tewḍa-dd taǧest x tgeldit n řweḥc. Uca zeɛfen deg iřes nsen s ssibbet n řeḥriq  
\v 11 uca ceqqfen deg Yisem n AREBBI n ijenwan s ssibbet n řeḥriq d ibuɛrusen nsen, \add maca\add* war tuben ca zi řexdayem nsen.   
\m
\v 12 Xenni ifarreɣ \bd lmalak wiss setta\bd* ṭṭawya nnes deg iɣzar ameqqran, \add iɣzar n\add* Lfuraṭ uca uẓɣen waman nnes, ařami issewjed abrid i ijeǧiden inni dd ɣa yasen zi manis dd-tneqqar tfuct. \x ◘ \xo 16:12 \xt Ica. 11:15\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Xenni ẓriɣ, aqa třata n řaryaḥ imengas am iqarqriwen \add ffɣen-dd\add* zeg uxenfuc n řhaycet u zeg uqemmum n řweḥc u zeg uqemmum n unabi issxarriqen,  
\v 14 maɣar nitni d řaryaḥ n ccwaṭen inni itteggen řeɛřamat i d igguren ɣar ijeǧiden n ddunect, maḥend ad ten ssmunen i umenɣi deg wass ameqqran n AREBBI, Amzemmar x kuřci. \x ◘ \xo 16:14 \xt 2 Ts. 2:9; Asa. 13:13; 17:14; 19:19, 20; 20:8. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 \qt “Xzar, Necc ad dd-aseɣ\qt*  
\m \qt am yijj n uceffar!\qt*  
\m \bdit Sseɛd\bdit* \qt n wenni i ɣa iqqimen ifaq,\qt*  
\m \qt wenni i ɣa iḥḍan arruḍ nnes\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima war iggur d aɛaryan,\qt*  
\m \qt war ittwaẓar useḍḥi nnes.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 16:15 \xt Mt. 24:43; Lk. 12:39; 1 Ts. 5:2; 2 Bṭ. 3:10; Asa. 3:3, 18. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Uca issmun i-ten ɣar wemcan umi ttřaɣan s Tɛibranit ‘Megiddu’.   
\b  
\m
\v 17 Xenni ifarreɣ \bd lmalak wiss sebɛa\bd* ṭṭawya nnes x řeɛwin uca tusa-dd ict n tmijja tejhed zi Zzawect Tameqqrant, zi zzat n řɛarc, teqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa ittwakemmeř!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 16:17 \xt Ica. 66:6; Asa. 21:6. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 Uca usin-dd wassamen d wajjajen, uca imsar ijj n wenhezzi n temmurt d ameqqran, war temsar ammu zeg wami iǧa bnadem di temmurt, ammu i imɣar. \x ◘ \xo 16:18 \xt Asa. 4:5; 8:5. \x*  
\v 19 Tandint tameqqrant tewḍa tebḍa x třata n tseqqar uca marra tineddam n řegnus hedment uca AREBBI iɛqeř x \add tendint\add* tameqqrant Babil, ḥima ad as iwc řkas n binu n tefqeḥt n weɣḍab nnes. \x ◘ \xo 16:19 \xt Izhd. 75:9; Irm. 25:15; Asa. 14:8, 10; 18:5. \x*  
\v 20 Uca kuř tagzirt tarweř, war ttwifin ca idurar \add ɛad\add*,  
\v 21 wḍan-dd ibquqen imeqqranen n tebruri zeg ujenna x iwdan, tuɣa ddqeř nsen anect n ict n ‘talint’, uca iwdan ceqqfen di AREBBI zi ssibbet n jjriḥect n tebruri, minzi jjriḥect nnes tuɣa temɣar aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 16:21 \xt Asa. 11:19; 16:9, 11. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 17
\s1 Tamɣart i iqqimen x řweḥc  
\m
\v 1 \bd Uca yusa-dd ijjen zi sebɛa n lmalakat\bd*, tinni ɣar iǧa sebɛa n ṭṭawyat, issiweř akidi, inna:  
\b  
\m \qt “As-dd, ad ac ssecneɣ řḥukm\qt*  
\m \qt x temɣart n farq-ccɣeř\qt*  
\m \qt i iqqimen x waṭṭas n waman,\qt*   
\m
\v 2 \qt tenni zi ssfesden ijeǧiden n temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt ixef nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt uca marra imezdaɣ n temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt scaren s binu n farq-ccɣeř nnes.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 Indeh ayi di Arruḥ ɣar řexřa uca ẓriɣ ict n tmeṭṭut tenya x ijj n řweḥc azeggʷaɣ iḥedqen, iccuren s ismawen n ttekfir, tuɣa ɣares sebɛa n izeǧifen d ɛecra n waccawen. \x ◘ \xo 17:3 \xt Asa. 13:1; 17:8. \x*  
\v 4 Tuɣa tameṭṭut tyarḍ taqendurt turjuwanit d tazeggwaɣt iḥedqen teqqen s wureɣ d yeẓra iɣřan d tyaqutin. Tuɣa ɣares deg ufus nnes ijj n uɣarraf n wureɣ iccur s řexmej u s nnɛi n farq-ccɣeř nnes. \x ◘ \xo 17:4 \xt Asa. 18:16. \x*  
\v 5 Ittwari x tenyart nnes ijj n isem: ‘Ssirr n Babil tameqqrant, yemmatsent n temɣarin n farq-ccɣeř d marra nnɛawat n temmurt’. \x ◘ \xo 17:5 \xt 2 Ts. 2:7. \x*  
\v 6 Uca ẓriɣ tameṭṭut tescar s idammen n imqeddasen u s idammen n yinni icehhden x Yasuɛ. Ařami tt ẓriɣ, ttbehteɣ aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Asa. 18:24. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Inna ayi lmalak: “Mayemmi tᵉttbehted? Necc ad cek ssargbeɣ x ssirr n tmeṭṭut d řweḥc s sebɛa n izeǧifen d ɛecra n waccawen, wenni tt yarebbun.   
\m
\v 8 Řweḥc i teẓrid, d wenni tuɣa d wenni war iǧin, ad igeɛɛed zi řebḥar, ad iweddar. Uca ad tbehten imezdaɣ n temmurt, inni isem nsen war ittwazemmem ca deg Wedlis ittwanḍen n Tudart zeg wami ittwagg dsas n ddunect, \add ad tbehten\add* xmi ɣa ẓaren řweḥc wenni tuɣa, d wenni war iǧin, \add ɛad\add* ad dd-iqarreb. \x ◘ \xo 17:8 \xt Uf. 32:32; Ica. 23:13; Fil. 4:3; Asa. 13:8. \x*  
\v 9 Aqa da řmeɛna \add nnes\add* i wenni ɣar teǧa řefhamet: sebɛa n izeǧifen aqa d sebɛa n idurar min xef teqqim tmeṭṭut. \x ◘ \xo 17:9 \xt Asa. 13:1, 18. \x*  
\v 10 Aqa-ten uřa d sebɛa n ijeǧiden, xemsa zzaysen wḍan, ijjen aqa iǧa \add ɛad\add*, d wenneɣni aqa-t ɛad war dd-yusi. Mařa netta ad dd-yas, ad as immewc drus \add n řweqt\add* i iqqimen \add ɛad\add*.  
\v 11 Uca řhaycet d řweḥc nni dd-yiwi u war iǧi d wenni, \add řhaycet nni\add* aqa-tt d \add ajeǧid\add* wiss tmenya, \add maca\add* ad teffeɣ zi sebɛa nni uca ad thellek.   
\m
\v 12 Ɛecra n waccawen i teẓrid, aqa d ɛecra n ijeǧiden, war ṭṭifen tagelda ɛad, maca ad ṭṭfen ṣṣulṭa n ijeǧiden řqedd n ict n tsaɛɛet ak-d řweḥc. \x ◘ \xo 17:12 \xt Dan. 7:20; Asa. 13:1. \x*  
\v 13 Nitni ɣarsen array d ijjen, ad wcen jjehd nsen d ṣṣulṭa nsen i řweḥc.  
\v 14 Ina ad mmenɣen ak-d Izmar uca Izmar ad xasen iɣřeb minzi Netta d Sidi x \add marra\add* isiditen d Ujeǧid x \add marra\add* ijeǧiden, u inni akides \add iǧan\add* aqa-ten d inni ittwařaɣan d yinni ittwafarzen d imtiqqan.” \x ◘ \xo 17:14 \xt 1 Tim. 6:15; Asa. 16:14; 19:16. \x*   
\m
\v 15 Inna ayi \add ɛawed\add*: “Aman i teẓrid i x teqqim temɣart n farq-ccɣeř, aqa aten d řegnus, d ibarruten n řɣaci, d ccuɛub, d iřsawen. \x ◘ \xo 17:15 \xt Ica. 8:7. \x*   
\m
\v 16 Uca ɛecra n waccawen i teẓrid x řweḥc, nitni ad carhen tamɣart n farq-ccɣeř ad tt areddǧen, ad tt arren d taɛeryant, ad ccen aysum nnes, ad tt sscemḍen s tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 17:16 \xt Asa. 18:8. \x*  
\v 17 Maɣar AREBBI iwca asen deg wuřawen nsen ḥima ad ggen nneyyet \add n řweḥc\add*, u maḥend ad tt ggen s array d ijjen, uca ad wcen tagelda nsen i řweḥc ař ɣa ttwakemmřen awařen n AREBBI.   
\m
\v 18 Uca tameṭṭut i teẓrid, nettat d tandint tameqqrant, tenni ɣar teǧa tgelda x ijeǧiden n temmurt.” \x ◘ \xo 17:18 \xt Asa. 16:19. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 18
\s1 Aweṭṭu n Babil  
\m
\v 1 Awarni as ẓriɣ \bd ijj n lmalak nneɣni ihekkwa-dd zeg ujenna\bd*, ɣares ṣṣulṭa tameqqrant, uca ṭṭya n uɛuǧi nnes tegga tafawt kuřci i temmurt.  
\v 2 Netta iřaɣa s tmijja tejhed, iqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa tewḍa, tewḍa \+tl tendint\+tl* tameqqrant Babil,\qt*  
\m \qt tedweř d tazeddiɣt i ccwaṭen\qt*  
\m \qt d řeḥbes i kuř řaryaḥ amengus amenɛi,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:2 \xt Ica. 13:21; 21:9; 34:11, 14; Irm. 50:39; 51:8; Asa. 14:8. \x*   
\m
\v 3 \qt minzi tessxeǧeḍ binu n farq-ccɣeř nnes\qt*  
\m \qt i marra řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt u minzi ijeǧiden n temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ssfesden ixef nsen zzayes,\qt*  
\m \qt u minzi isebbaben n temmurt\qt*  
\m \qt dewřen d twajjar\qt*  
\m \qt s jjehd n uṭemmes nnes n wagra.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:3 \xt Asa. 14:8; 17:2. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Uca sřiɣ i tmijja nneɣni třaɣa-dd zeg ujenna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ffeɣ zzayes, \+tl a\+tl* řgens inu,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima war ttiřin ddnub nnes x yiri nnec\qt*  
\m \qt uca war tkessid zi jjrayeḥ nnes,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:4 \xt Amz. 19:12; Ica. 48:20; 52:11; Irm. 51:6, 45; 2 Kur. 6:17. \x*   
\m
\v 5 \qt minzi ddnub nnes aqa iwḍen ɣar ujenna,\qt*  
\m \qt uca AREBBI aqa iɛqeř x řmuɛṣiyyet nnes.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:5 \xt Asa. 16:19. \x*   
\m
\v 6 \qt Arrem-dd xas\qt*  
\m \qt am mammec dd-tarra nettat,\qt*  
\m \qt arrem-dd xas s uḍeffus\qt*  
\m \qt ɛlaḥsab řexdayem nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt xeǧeḍ as s uḍeffus deg uɣarraf\qt*  
\m \qt nni tuɣa txeǧeḍ nettat.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:6 \xt Asa. 14:10. \x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Xeřfem as-dd aɛeddeb d wecḍan\qt*  
\m \qt anect tuɣa nettat tessɛuǧi\qt*  
\m \qt u tessgeɛɛed ixef nnes\qt*  
\m \qt minzi tenna deg wuř nnes:\qt*  
\m \qt ‘Aqa qqimeɣ am tjeǧidt,\qt*  
\m \qt war ǧiɣ d tajjač,\qt*  
\m \qt uca acḍan war t ẓarreɣ ca!’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:7 \xt Ica. 47:8. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 S uyenni deg ijj n wass ad xas wḍant marra jjrayeḥ nnes: řmewt, acḍan d řaẓ, uca ad tᵉttwacmeḍ di tmessi, minzi SIDI, d wenni xas i ɣa iḥekmen, aqa ijhed. \x ◘ \xo 18:8 \xt 2 Ts. 2:8; Asa. 17:16. \x*   
\m
\v 9 \bd Ijeǧiden n temmurt\bd*, inni kides iggin farq-ccɣeř u ssgeɛɛden ixef nsen, ad xas run, ad xas wten agejdur xmi ɣa ẓaren ddexxan n tmessi nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:9 \xt Asa. 17:2; 18:3, 18. \x*  
\v 10 Nitni ad qqimen bedden ɣar řaggʷaj zi teggʷudi n uɛeddeb nnes, qqaren:  
\b  
\m \bdit ‘Uct, uct, uct, xam, a tandint tameqqrant\bdit*,  
\m \qt Babil, tandint ijehden,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi aqa yusa-dd řḥukm nnem\qt*  
\m \bdit deg ict n tsaɛɛet\bdit*!’” \x ◘ \xo 18:10 \xt Ica. 21:9; Irm. 51:1; Asa. 14:8. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 \bd Isebbaben n temmurt\bd* ad xas run, ad ceḍnen, minzi uřa d ijj war issiɣ ɛad sseřɛet nsen:  
\v 12 sseřɛet n wureɣ d nnuqart d yeẓra yiɣřan d tyaqutin d řeqṭen d arjuwani d řeḥrir azeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d ɛřam kuř akeccuḍ ittfuḥen d ɛřam kuř řeqcuɛ zi řɛaj d ɛřam kuř řeqcuɛ zeg ukeccuḍ iɣřan d nnḥas d wuzzař d řmarmur \f ◼ \fr 18:12 \ft \+fk řɛaj\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘acciwen n řfiř’.\f*  
\v 13 d řqarfa d řebxur d mirru d jjawi d binu d zzect n zzitun d aren n ssmid d wuǧi d yeysan d ikarruten uřa d arrimat d řeɛmur n iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 18:13 \xt Ḥiz. 27:13. \x*  
\v 14 Aqa řɣiǧet i di tuɣa ittmeẓri řeɛmar nnem, aqa tiggʷej xam, uřa d marra min tuɣa ɣarem d agřa d min ittissiqen, aqa iweddar, war t tẓarred ɛemmarṣ \add ɛad\add*.  
\v 15 Isebbaben n řeḥwayej-a, inni idewřen zzaysent d twajjar, war tent ttifen ɛad, uca ad qqimen ɣar řaggʷaj zi teggʷudi n uɛeddeb nnes, am ttrun u am ceṭṭnen,  
\v 16 ad inin:  
\b  
\m \bdit “Uct, uct\bdit* \bdit xam\bdit*, \bdit a cem,\bdit* \bdit tandint tameqqrant\bdit*  
\m \qt i yarḍen řeqṭen d arjuwani\qt*  
\m \qt d azeggwaɣ iḥedqen iqqen s wureɣ\qt*  
\m \qt d yeẓra iɣřan d tyaqutin,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:16 \xt Asa. 17:4. \x*   
\m
\v 17 \qt s minzi\qt* \bdit deg ict n tsaɛɛet\bdit*  
\m \qt aqa iweddar wagřa ameqqran nni!”\qt*  
\b  
\m Marra inni ineddhen iɣarruba d marra inni ittekken \add x řebḥar\add* deg iɣarruba d marra ibeḥriyyen d marra inni ittsebbaben di řebḥar qqimen bedden ɣar řaggʷaj.  
\v 18 Nitni sɣuyyen umi ẓrin ddexxan n tmessi nnes, nnan:  
\b  
\m \qt “Wi izemmaren ad imqudda ak-d tendint-a tameqqrant?”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:18 \xt Ica. 34:10; Asa. 13:4; 18:9. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Ssuyusen ucař x izeǧifen nsen uca sɣuyen, am ttrun u am ttecḍinen, nnan:  
\b  
\m \bdit “Uct, uct xam,\bdit* \bdit a cem,\bdit* \bdit tandint tameqqrant\bdit*  
\m \qt nni di dewřen d twajjar\qt*  
\m \qt marra inni ɣar iǧa iɣarruba di řebḥar,\qt*  
\m \qt s ubarru n wagřa nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi\qt* \bdit deg ict n tsaɛɛet\bdit* \qt tweddar!”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 \qt “Farḥet zzayes, \+tl a\+tl* ajenna,\qt*  
\m \qt u \+tl kenniw, a\+tl* imqeddasen d rrusul d inabiyyen,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi AREBBI aqa issuffeɣ-dd řeḥkamet nnes xas!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:20 \xt Asa. 19:2. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 21 Uca ijj zi lmalakat nni issgeɛɛed ijj n weẓru ameqqran anect n teṣḍart n tsirt, inḍar i-t di řebḥar, iqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ammu s jjehd ad tᵉmmenḍar\qt*  
\m \qt tandint tameqqrant Babil\qt*  
\m \qt uca war tᵉttwifi ɛad ɛemmarṣ!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:21 \xt Irm. 51:64. \x*   
\m
\v 22 \qt Řḥess n lharpa d usuḍi deg\qt*  
\m \bdit uyicc n icarri,\bdit*  
\m \qt d řḥess n ɛřam kuř aɣennej\qt*  
\m \qt u n yinni ittsuḍen di řbuq,\qt*  
\m \qt war ittwaseř ɛad dayem.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:22 \xt Irm. 25:10; Ḥiz. 26:13. \x*   
\m
\v 23 \qt Ɛemmarṣ ad dayem tᵉttwaẓar ɛad\qt*  
\m \qt ṭṭya n řefnar,\qt*  
\m \qt uca uřa d řḥess n wesři\qt*  
\m \qt d řḥess n tesřit\qt*  
\m \qt war ittwaseř ɛad dayem.\qt*  
\m \qt Isebbaben nnem tuɣa aten\qt*  
\m \qt d imeqqranen n temmurt,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi s tseḥḥart nnem,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa txedɛed řegnus marra.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:23 \xt Irm. 7:34; 16:9; 25:10. \x*   
\m
\v 24 \qt Aqa ittwaf dayem idammen\qt*  
\m \qt n inabiyyen d imqeddasen,\qt*  
\m \qt inni ittwanɣen di temmurt.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 18:24 \xt Amz. 4:10; Asa. 17:6. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 19
\s1 Iẓři x uweṭṭu n Babil  
\m
\v 1 Awarni as sřiɣ ijj n řḥess ameqqran n waṭṭas n řɣaci deg ujenna, nnan:  
\b  
\m \qt “Hallilu-Yah!\qt*  
\m \qt Asenjem d uɛuǧi d jjehd\qt*  
\m \qt aqa aten ɣar AREBBI nneɣ,\qt*   
\m
\v 2 \qt minzi řeḥkamat nnes\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl mɣir\+tl* d tidett d řḥeqq,\qt*  
\m \qt umi iḥaseb x temɣart n farq-ccɣeř,\qt*  
\m \qt tenni yareddǧen ddunect\qt*  
\m \qt s farq-ccɣeř nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt uca Netta yuɣa tasɣart\qt*  
\m \qt x idammen n imsexxaren nnes\qt*  
\m \qt i yumsen ɣar ifassen nnes.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:2 \xt Aɛwd. 32:43; Asa. 15:3; 16:7; 18:20. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 Nnan i \add umur\add* wiss tnayen:  
\b  
\m \qt “Hallilu-Yah!”\qt*  
\b  
\m Uca ad yaři ddexxan nnes ɣar ujenna i řebda qaɛ.\x ◘ \xo 19:3 \xt Ica. 34:10; Asa. 14:11; 18:18. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Uca arebɛa u-ɛicrin n imɣaren d arebɛa n imuddaren wḍan ɣar temmurt, sejden i AREBBI nneɣ wenni iqqimen x řɛarc, nnan:  
\b  
\m \qt “Amin, Hallilu-Yah!”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 Uca tusa-dd ict n tmijja zi řɛarc, tenna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Semɣarem AREBBI nneɣ, \+tl a\+tl* \+tl kenniw\+tl* marra imsexxaren nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt u marra inni itteggʷeden Isem nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt am umeẓyan am umeqqran!”\qt*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řemřac n Yezmar  
\m
\v 6 Uca sřiɣ aqa nnan am s tmijja n ubarru n řɣaci, am s řḥess n waṭṭas n waman, am s zzhir n wajjajen imeqqranen:  
\b  
\m \qt “Hallilu-Yah, minzi SIDI AREBBI,\qt*  
\m \qt Amzemmar x kuřci, aqa iḥekkem.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:6 \xt Asa. 11:17; Asa. 14:2\x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Ejj ad nfarḥ, ad nesřiwřiw,\qt*  
\m \qt ad as negg aɛuǧi,\qt*  
\m \qt maɣar Urar n Yezmar yiweḍ-dd,\qt*  
\m \qt uca tamɣart nnes aqa tḥezzem,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:7 \xt Mt. 22:2; Lk. 14:16. \x*   
\m
\v 8 \qt uca temmewc as ad tyarḍ arruḍ\qt*  
\m \qt zi řqeṭṭan ifsusen izdigen ittissiqen,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi řqeṭṭan nni\qt*  
\m \qt d řexdayem iseggden n imqeddasen.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Nitni nnan ayi:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ari:\qt* \bdit Sseɛd\bdit* \qt n yinni ittwaɛarḍen\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar umensi n Wurar n Izmar.’\qt*  
\b  
\m \add Xas uca\add* inna ayi ca n yijjen:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ina d awařen n tidett n AREBBI.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt Asa. 21:5. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 Uca wḍiɣ as ɣar iḍaren nnes ḥima ad t ɛebdeɣ, \add maca\add* netta inna ayi:  
\b  
\m \qt “Lla, \+tl war ttegg ca man aya!\+tl* Aqa necc d amsexxar amɛacar am cek d aytmac inni ɣar teǧa cchadet n Yasuɛ. Ɛebdet AREBBI, minzi cchadet n Yasuɛ nettat d Arruḥ n min ittwanabben.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:10 \xt Řex. 10:26; 14:14; Asa. 22:9. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Amnay s uyis d acemřař  
\m
\v 11 \add Awarni aya\add* ẓriɣ ajenna innurzem, u xzar, aqa din ijj n uyis d acemřař d Wenni xas inyin, qqaren as ‘Dayes řaman!’, ‘Dayes tidett!’, uca Netta ad iḥaseb u ad immneɣ s tsegda. \x ◘ \xo 19:11 \xt Asa. 6:2. \x*  
\v 12 Tuɣa tiṭṭawin nnes amecnaw iḥudaq n tmessi, uca ɣares x uzeǧif nnes aṭṭas n ttijan, uca yura xas Isem i war t issin ḥed mɣir Netta waha. \x ◘ \xo 19:12 \xt Asa. 1:14. \x*  
\v 13 Tuɣa yarḍ ijj n useřham ittwaruccen s idammen, uca wa d Isem nnes: \bd ‘Awař n AREBBI’\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 19:13 \xt Ica. 63:1; Yḥ. 1:1. \x*  
\v 14 Řɛeskarat n ujenna ḍfaren t-i-dd x yeysan icemřařen, arḍen řqeṭṭan d acemřař izdig. \x ◘ \xo 19:14 \xt Mt. 28:3; Asa. 4:4; 7:9. \x*  
\v 15 Ffɣen-dd řesyuf iqeḍɛen zeg iqemmumen nsen maḥend ad zzaysen nɣen řegnus, u Netta ad ten iḥḍa s uzeǧaḍ n wuzzař, u Netta \add simant nnes\add* ad iɛfes di tsirt n weɣḍab n AREBBI, Amzemmar x kuřci. \x ◘ \xo 19:15 \xt Izhd. 2:9; Ica. 63:3; Asa. 2:16, 27; 14:19, 20; 19:21. \x*  
\v 16 X warruḍ nnes u x tmeṣṣaḍin nnes yura xasen Isem-a: \bd ‘Ajeǧid x \+bdit marra\+bdit* ijeǧiden’, ‘Sidi x \+bdit marra\+bdit* řḥukkam’.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 19:16 \xt 1 Tim. 6:15; Asa. 17:14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 17 Uca ẓriɣ ijj n lmalak nneɣni ibedd di tfuct. Netta iřaɣa s jjehd, inna i marra ijḍaḍ iṭṭawen di řwesṭ n ujenna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Asettiw-d, munettiw-dd\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar umensi ameqqran n AREBBI,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 19:17 \xt Irm. 12:9; Ḥiz. 39:17. \x*   
\m
\v 18 \qt ḥima ad teccem aysum n ijeǧiden\qt*  
\m \qt d weysum n imeqqranen x wařef\qt*  
\m \qt d weysum n yinni ijehden\qt*  
\m \qt d weysum n iysan d yinni xasen inyin,\qt*  
\m \qt d weysum n iḥurriyyen d isemɣan,\qt*  
\m \qt am n imeẓyanen am n imeqqranen.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Uca ẓriɣ řweḥc ak-d řɛeskarat nnes d ijeǧiden n temmurt d iɛeskarriyyen nsen, inni imunen ḥima ad mmenɣen ak-d Wenni inyin x uyis, u ak-d iɛeskariyyen nnes.  
\v 20 Aqa ittwaṭṭef řweḥc ak-d unabi issxarriqen, wenni iggin zzates řeɛřamat nni zi tuɣa iɣecc inni iksin řmarka n řweḥc uca sejden i řexyař nnes. Nitni s tnayen idsen ttwammenḍaren di řebḥar n tmessi ittcefcufen ɛawed s řecbareyyet. \x ◘ \xo 19:20 \xt Aɛwd. 13:2; Dan. 7:11; Mt. 24:24; Asa. 13:12, 13, 15, 16; 16:14; 20:10. \x*  
\v 21 Maca wi iqqimen ttwanɣen s wuzzař i dd-ikkin zeg uqemmum n wenni inyin x uyis. Uca marra ijḍaḍ ittkeccaḍen jjiwnen s weysum nsen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 20
\s1 Tageldit n ařef n iseggʷusa  
\m
\v 1 Uca ẓriɣ ijj n lmalak nneɣni ihwa-dd zeg ujenna, ɣares tasarut n tesraft i iǧan sadu i temmurt d ict n ssnesřet tameqqrant deg ufus nnes. \x ◘ \xo 20:1 \xt Asa. 1:18. \x*  
\v 2 Netta iṭṭef řhaycet, afiɣar awessar, wenni d ibřis d cciṭan uca icarf i-t i yijj n řqedd n wařef n iseggʷusa, \x ◘ \xo 20:2 \xt 2 Bṭ. 2:4; Asa. 12:9. \x*  
\v 3 uca inḍar i-t di tesraft sadu temmurt, ibelleɛ xas uca igga xas acemmiɛ, ḥima war ittɣecci ɛad řegnus. Awarni man aya ad ittwaḍřeq ɣar cwayt n řweqt. \x ◘ \xo 20:3 \xt Asa. 16:14, 16; 20:8. \x*   
\m
\v 4 Necc ẓriɣ řekrasi n ijeǧiden uca nitni ssɣimin ixef nsen xasen, uca immewc asen řḥukm. Aqa řeɛmur-a - n yinni umi kksen izeǧifen nsen di ṭṭweɛ n cchadet n Yasuɛ d wawař n AREBBI, war sejden i řweḥc uřa i řexyař, war ṭṭifen ca řmarka x tenyart nsen uřa deg ufus nsen - \add aqa řeɛmur-a\add* ddaren u ḥekmen ak-d Lmasiḥ ařef iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 20:4 \xt Asa. 6:9, 11; 13:12, 15, 16. \x*   
\m
\v 5 Ta d tanukra tamezwarut.  
\v 6 \bd Sseɛd\bd* d umqeddas n wenni i ɣa iṭṭfen tasɣart di tnukra tamezwarut. Řmewt wiss tnayen war ɣares tiři bu ṣṣulṭa xasen, maca nitni ad iřin d ikehhanen n AREBBI u n Lmasiḥ uca ad kis ḥekmen ařef n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 20:6 \xt Ica. 61:6; 1 Bṭ. 2:9; Asa. 1:6; 5:10. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řḥukm x cciṭan ameqqran  
\m
\v 7 Xmi ɣa iqfeř ařef n iseggʷusa, ad ittwaḍřeq cciṭan zi řeḥbes nnes,  
\v 8 uca ad dd-iffeɣ ḥima ad iɣecc marra řegnus inni iǧan ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura n temmurt, \add Ha\add*juj d Majuj, ad ten issmun i umenɣi, u řqedd nsen am yejdi n řebḥar. \f ◼ \fr 20:8 \ft \+fk Hajuj\ft  - niɣ ‘Juj’, niɣ ‘Xux’, niɣ ‘Gug’. \fk Majuj\ft  - niɣ ‘Maxux’, niɣ ‘Magug’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:8 \xt Ḥiz. 38:2; 39:1; Asa. 16:14. \x*  
\v 9 Ḥarrcen-dd zi ṭṭarf n temmurt uca nnḍen as i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n imqeddasen d tendint iɛizzen, uca tewḍa-dd tmessi zeg ujenna, zi \add zzat\add* AREBBI, uca tecca i-ten.  
\v 10 Uca ibřis, wenni tuɣa ten iɣwan, aqa immenḍar di řebḥar n tmessi ittcefcufen s řecbareyyet mani iǧa řweḥc d unabi issxarriqen uca ad ttwaɛeddben ass d ǧiřet i řebda qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 20:10 \xt Dan. 7:11; Asa. 14:10; 19:20. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řḥukm x imettinen  
\m
\v 11 Uca ẓriɣ ijj n řɛarc d ameqqran d acemřař d Wenni xas iqqimen, aqa zi arendad n uɣembub nnes tarweř temmurt d ujenna, \add maca\add* war d asen iqqim bu wemcan.  
\v 12 Necc ẓriɣ imettinen bedden zzat i řɛarc, imeqqranen d imeẓyanen. Aqa nnurzmen idlisen \add ittwanḍen\add* uca innurzem wedlis \add ittwanḍen\add* nneɣni, \add Adlis ittwanḍen\add* n Řḥukm. Uca ittwaḥkem x imettinen zi min yuran deg wedlis \add ittwanḍen\add* x řeḥsab n řexdayem nsen. \x ◘ \xo 20:12 \xt Uf. 32:32; Izhd. 62:13; 69:29; Irm. 17:10; 32:19; Dan. 7:9-12; Mt. 16:27; Rum. 2:6; 14:12; 2 Kur. 5:10; Gal. 6:5; Fil. 4:3; Asa. 2:23; 3:5. \x*  
\v 13 Uca řebḥar iwca imettinen inni tuɣa aten dayes, uca řmewt d řaxart wcint imettinen inni tuɣa aten daysent, uca ittwaḥkem xasen, kuř ijjen anect n řexdayem nnes.  
\v 14 Řmewt d řaxart mmenḍarent di řebḥar n tmessi. Ta d řmewt wiss tnayen.  
\v 15 Mařa ittwaf ḥed war ittwazemmem deg Wedlis \add ittwanḍen\add* n Tudart, immenḍar di řebḥar n tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 20:15 \xt Asa. 13:8\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Ajenna n jdid d temmurt n jdid  
\m
\v 1 Uca ẓriɣ ajenna n jdid d ict n temmurt n jdid, maɣar ajenna amezwaru d temmurt tamezwarut tuɣa ɛdun, řebḥar war iqqim ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 21:1 \xt Ica. 65:17; 66:22; 2 Bṭ. 3:13. \x*  
\v 2 Necc ẓriɣ tandint iqeddsen, Urcalim n jdid, tehwa-dd zeg ujenna zi zzat AREBBI, tegga am tesřit izehhjen i wesři. \x ◘ \xo 21:2 \xt Asa. 3:12; 21:10. \x*  
\v 3 Uca sřiɣ ict n tmijja tᵉttřaɣa-dd zeg ujenna s jjehd:  
\b  
\m \qt “Xẓar, Aqiḍun n AREBBI\qt*  
\m \qt aqa-tt jar iwdan,\qt*  
\m \qt uca Netta ad ɣarsen izdeɣ.\qt*  
\m \qt Nitni ad iřin d řgens nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt uca AREBBI simant nnes\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ad\+tl* ɣarsen \+tl yiři\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad yiři d AREBBI nsen.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:3 \xt Ḥiz. 43:7. \x*   
\m
\v 4 \qt Ad asen issiẓeɣ kuř imeṭṭan\qt*  
\m \qt zi tiṭṭawin nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt uca war tᵉttiři ɛad řmewt\qt*  
\m \qt d wecḍan d ucetci d řeḥriq.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:4 \xt Ica. 25:8; Asa. 7:17. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 U xmi ggureɣ, inna ayi wenni iqqimen x řɛarc:  
\b  
\m \qt “Xẓar, ad ggeɣ marra d jdid!”\qt*  
\b  
\m \add Xas uca\add* inna ayi:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ari: Awařen-a aqa daysen řaman d tidett.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:5 \xt Ica. 43:19; 2 Kur. 5:17; Asa. 4:2; 19:9; 20:11. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 Netta inna ayi:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa ittwakemmeř.\qt*  
\m \qt Necc d Alif u Necc d Taw,\qt*  
\m \qt Necc d Beddu d Akemmeř.\qt*  
\m \qt Wenni iffuden ad as wceɣ\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl ad isu\+tl* baṭeř\qt*  
\m \qt zi řɛunṣar n Waman n Tudart.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:6 \xt Ica. 41:4; 44:6; 55:1; Asa. 1:8; 16:17; 22:13. \x*   
\m
\v 7 \qt Wi ɣa iɣellben ad iwart man aya,\qt*  
\m \qt uca Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt u netta ad yiři d mmi.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:7 \xt Zak. 8:8; Ɛbr. 8:10. \x*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Maca inni ittcekkan, d lkuffar,\qt*  
\m \qt d iɛeffanen, d imexmaj,\qt*  
\m \qt d yinni ineqqen, d yinni iggin taseḥḥart,\qt*  
\m \qt d ayt n farq-ccɣeř\qt*  
\m \qt d yinni iɛebbden l’aṣnam\qt*  
\m \qt d marra ayt n bu-ixarriqen,\qt*  
\m \qt ad tiři tesɣart nsen\qt*  
\m \qt di řebḥar ittcefcufen\qt*  
\m \qt s tmessi d řecbareyyet,\qt*  
\m \qt ta d řmewt wiss tnayen.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:8 \xt Asa. 20:14, 15; 22:15. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Urcalim n jdid  
\m
\v 9 Uca yusa-dd ijjen zi sebɛa n lmalakat, tinni ɣarsent sebɛa n ṭṭawyat ccurent s sebɛa n jjrayeḥ tineggura, issiweř akidi, inna:  
\b  
\m \qt “As-dd, ad ac ssecneɣ tasřit, tamɣart n Yezmar.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 21:9 \xt Asa. 15:6, 7. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 Indeh ayi di Arruḥ ɣar ijj n wedrar d ameqqran yuɛřan aṭṭas uca isscen ayi tandint iqeddsen, Urcalim, am dd-tehwa zeg ujenna, zi zzat n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 21:10 \xt Ɛbr. 12:22; Asa. 1:10; 21:2. \x*  
\v 11 Aɛuǧi n AREBBI tuɣa ɣares, uca ṭṭya nnes tᵉttissiq am yiẓra iɣřan aṭṭas, am weẓru n yaspis nni dd-iḍharen am ukristal.  
\v 12 Iquwwar as dd ijj n weɣbar d ameqqran yuɛřa, ɣares tenɛac n tewwura u tenɛac n lmalakat \add tuɣa ttbeddant\add* ɣar tiwwura. U ttwarin ismawen \add x tiwwura nni\add*, aqa ismawen n tenɛac n tqebbař n Israil.  
\v 13 \add Aqa din\add* třata n tewwura ɣar manis d tneqqar tfuct u ɣar ccamal třata n tewwura u ɣar ljanub třata n tewwura u \add aqa din\add* třata n tewwura ɣar mani tɣeǧi tfuct.  
\v 14 Aɣbar n tendint ibedd x tenɛac n dsusa ttwarin xasen tenɛac n ismawen n rrusul n Mmis \add n AREBBI\add*. \x ◘ \xo 21:14 \xt Afa. 2:20. \x*   
\m
\v 15 Wenni tuɣa akidi issawařen, ɣares ijj n uɣanim n řeɛbar ḥima ad \add zzayes\add* iɛbar tandint d weɣbar nnes. \x ◘ \xo 21:15 \xt Ḥiz. 40:3; Zak. 1:18. \x*  
\v 16 Tandint tuɣa temmars \add din am\add* ijj n ukwadrun, tazuggart nnes am tiru nnes. Netta iɛbar tandint s \add uɣanim nnes\add* n řeɛbar: tenɛac-ařef n ‘istadiyyen’, \add ɛřaḥař ařfayen u mitayen kilumitr\add*. Tazuggart nnes d tiru nnes d řuɛřa nnes d icten.  
\v 17 Iɛbar aɣbar nnes: mya u-arebɛa u-rebɛin n iɣaǧen, aqa-t d řqedd n ijj n bnadem, aqa-t n lmalak.  
\v 18 Aɣbar nnes ggin t s yaspis, u tandint ggint s wureɣ iṣfan, ittban am zzaj iṣfan.  
\v 19 Dsusa n weɣbar n tendint tuɣa ttwazewwqen kuřci s iẓra iɣřan. Tuɣa dsas amezwaru n \add weẓru n\add* yaspis, wenni wiss tnayen n ṣaffir, wenni wiss třata n xalcidun, wenni wiss arebɛa n smiralda,  
\v 20 wenni d wiss xemsa n sarduniks, wenni wiss setta n sardiyus, wenni wiss sebɛa n weẓru n wureɣ, wenni wiss tmenya n biril, wenni wiss tesɛa n tupas, wenni wiss ɛecra n krisupras, wenni wiss ḥiṭac n yazint uca wenni wiss tenɛac n umetist.  
\v 21 Tenɛac n tewwura d tenɛac n tyaqutin, ict ict. Kuř icten \add zi tewwura\add* nni tuɣa zeg ict n tyaqut. Maca abrid yiriwen n tendint tuɣa-t n wureɣ iṣfan, am zzaj iṣfan.   
\m
\v 22 War ẓriɣ ca Zzawect dayes minzi SIDI AREBBI, Amzemmar x kuřci, Netta Simant nnes d Zzawect nnes.  
\v 23 Izmar d tendint war ḥdajen ca tafuct uřa d taziri, ḥima ad xas ssarɣent, minzi aɛuǧi n AREBBI yareqq dayes uca Izmar d Řefnar nnes. \x ◘ \xo 21:23 \xt Ica. 60:19; Zak. 14:7. \x*  
\v 24 Řegnus ad uyuren s tfawt nnes uca ijeǧiden n temmurt ad ɣares ssidfen aɛuǧi \add nsen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 21:24 \xt Ica. 60:3. \x*  
\v 25 Tiwwura nnes war ttwaqqnent ɛemmarṣ s uziř, minzi ǧiřet war tᵉttɣimi ca din. \x ◘ \xo 21:25 \xt Ica. 60:11; Asa. 22:5. \x*  
\v 26 Nitni ad awyen ɣares aɛuǧi d ccan n řegnus.  
\v 27 Ɛemmarṣ ad dayes tadef ca n řḥajjet tamengust niɣ wenni iggin nnɛawat niɣ wenni issxarriqen, mɣir inni ittwazemmemen deg Wedlis \add ittwanḍen\add* n Yezmar waha. \x ◘ \xo 21:27 \xt Uf. 32:32; Izhd. 69:29; Fil. 4:3; Asa. 3:5; 13:8; 20:12. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 22
\s1 Iɣzar n Waman Iddaren  
\m
\v 1 Uca netta isscen ayi ijj n iɣzar izdig n Waman Iddaren, d amezdag, iṣfa am ukristal, i dd-itteffɣen zi řɛarc n AREBBI u n Yezmar. \x ◘ \xo 22:1 \xt Ḥiz. 47:1; Zak. 14:8. \x*  
\v 2 Di řwesṭ n wazzay nnes, x tma-ya u x tma nni n iɣzar, tuɣa Tacejjart n Tudart tenni tessenḍay řɣiǧet tenɛac \add n twařawin\add*. Di mkuř ayur tettic řɣiǧet nnes d tifray nnes i usgenfu n řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 22:2 \xt Ḥiz. 47:1-12; Asa. 2:7. \x*  
\v 3 War dayes tᵉttiři ɛad nneɛřet. Ad dayes yiři řɛarc n AREBBI u n Yezmar uca imsexxaren nnes ad xas sexxaren.  
\v 4 Nitni ad ẓaren udem nnes, Isem nnes ad yiři x tenyarin nsen. \x ◘ \xo 22:4 \xt Asa. 3:12. \x*  
\v 5 War din tᵉttiři ǧiřet uca nitni war tteḥdijen ɛad ṭṭya n řefnarat niɣ n tfawin niɣ n tfawt n tfuct, minzi SIDI AREBBI ad asen igg tafawt uca ad yiři d Ajeǧid nsen i řebda qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 22:5 \xt Ica. 60:19; Zak. 14:7; Asa. 21:23. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 \add Xas uca\add* inna ayi:  
\b  
\m \qt “Awařen-a daysen řaman d tidett!\qt*  
\m \qt SIDI, AREBBI n Arruḥ n inabiyyen iqeddsen,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa issekk lmalak nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad isscen i imsexxaren nnes\qt*  
\m \qt min i ɣa yiřin deɣya.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:6 \xt Asa. 1:1; 19:9; 21:5. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 \bdit “Xzar Necc ad dd-aseɣ deɣya!\bdit*  
\m \bdit Sseɛd\bdit* \qt n wenni ittᵉṭṭfen\qt*  
\m \qt deg wawařen n nnubuwat\qt*  
\m \qt n Wedlis-a \+tl ittwanḍen\+tl*.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:7 \xt Asa. 1:3. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Necc, Yuḥanna, aqa ẓriɣ u sřiɣ timesřayin-a. Uca řami tent ẓriɣ u sřiɣ, wḍiɣ ɣar iḍaren n lmalak wenni d ayi issecnen timesřayin-a, ḥima ad \add as\add* ɛebdeɣ.  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* netta inna ayi:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ḥḍa, lla, war ttegg man aya,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl maɣar\+tl* necc d amsexxar amɛacar nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt u n aytmac, inabiyyen, uřa n yinni ittᵉṭṭfen\qt*  
\m \qt deg wawařen n Wedlis-a \+tl ittwanḍen\+tl*.\qt*  
\m \qt Ɛebdet AREBBI!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:9 \xt Řex. 10:26; 14:14; Asa. 19:10. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 \add Xas uca\add* inna ayi:  
\b  
\m \qt “War ttegg acemmiɛ x wawařen i ittwanabben\qt*  
\m \qt deg Wedlis-a \+tl ittwanḍen\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt minzi řweqt aqa tiweḍ-dd.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:10 \xt Dan. 8:26; 12:4; Asa. 1:3. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 \qt “Wenni itteggen min war iseggden,\qt*  
\m \qt ad igg min war iseggden ktar,\qt*  
\m \qt amengus ad idweř d amengus ktar,\qt*  
\m \qt amseggad ad igg tasegda ktar\qt*  
\m \qt uca amqeddas ad idweř d amqeddas ktar.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 \bdit “Xzar, Necc ad dd-aseɣ deɣya\bdit*  
\m \qt uca řmunet inu aqa-tt akidi,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad xeǧṣeɣ kuř ijjen\qt*  
\m \qt anect n řxedmet nnes.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:12 \xt Izhd. 62:13; Irm. 17:10; 32:19; Mt. 16:27; Rum. 2:6; 14:12; 1 Kur. 3:8; 2 Kur. 5:10; Gal. 6:5; Asa. 2:23. \x*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Necc d Alif u Necc d Taw,\qt*  
\m \qt d Amezwaru d Aneggaru,\qt*  
\m \qt d Beddu d Akemmeř.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:13 \xt Ica. 41:4; 44:6; 48:12; Asa. 1:8; 21:6. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 “\bdit Sseɛd\bdit* \qt nsen i yinni itteggen tiweṣṣa nnes.\qt*  
\m \qt Ad ɣarsen tiři ṣṣulṭa x Tcejjart n Tudart\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad dd-adfen ɣar tendint\qt*  
\m \qt zi tewwura nnes.\qt*   
\m
\v 15 \qt Barra iǧan inni itteggen farq-ccɣeř\qt*  
\m \qt d yinni ineqqen\qt*  
\m \qt d yinni iɛebbden l’aṣnam\qt*  
\m \qt d yinni daysen řexmej\qt*  
\m \qt d yinni ittseḥḥaren d marra imwařawen\qt*  
\m \qt d inni itteggen min i dd-itteffɣen\qt*  
\m \qt zeg uxarriq.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:15 \xt 1 Kur. 6:10; Afa. 5:5; Kul. 3:5, 6. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 \qt “Necc, Yasuɛ, aqa ssekkeɣ lmalak inu\qt*  
\m \qt maḥend ad xawem iched man aya\qt*  
\m \qt zzat i tmesmunin.\qt*  
\m \qt Aqa d NECC, d Aẓwar d Zzariɛet n Dawud,\qt*  
\m \qt d Wenni akides,\qt*  
\m \qt d Itri n Řefjar yareqqen.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:16 \xt Ica. 11:10; Rum. 15:12; 2 Bṭ. 1:19; Asa. 1:1; 5:5. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 17 Arruḥ d tesřit qqaren:  
\b  
\m \bdit “As-dd!”\bdit*  
\b  
\m Uca ejj wenni t isřin, ad yini:  
\b  
\m \bdit “As-dd!”\bdit*  
\b  
\m \qt “D wenni ifuden, ejj i-t ad dd-yas,\qt*  
\m \qt ad isu Aman Iddaren baṭeř.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:17 \xt Ica. 55:1; Yḥ. 7:37\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 \qt “Necc cehhdeɣ i marra inni ittesřan\qt*  
\m \qt i wawařen n nnubuwa n Wedlis-a \+tl ittwanḍen\+tl*:\qt*  
\m \qt Mařa din ḥed wenni xasen i ɣa yarnin,\qt*  
\m \qt AREBBI ad xas yarni jjrayeḥ,\qt*  
\m \qt tinni ittwazemmemen deg wedlis-a.\qt*   
\m
\v 19 \qt Mařa ca n ijjen ikkes zeg wawařen\qt*  
\m \qt n Wedlis \+tl ittwanḍen\+tl* n nnubuwa-ya,\qt*  
\m \qt ad as ikkes AREBBI tasɣart nnes\qt*  
\m \qt zi Tcejjart n Tudart u zi Tendint iqeddsen.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 22:19 \xt Aɛwd. 4:2; 12:32; Awřn. 30:6; Asa. 13:8; 17:8. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Xmi Netta iched x man aya, inna:  
\b  
\m \bdit “Wah, Necc ad dd-aseɣ deɣya!”\bdit*  
\b  
\m \bdit “As-dd,\bdit* \qt \+tl a\+tl* SIDI Yasuɛ!”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 21 Arḍa n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ \add aqa-t\add* ak-d marra imqeddasen nnes. “Amin!”  
\b  
\m  
\m Aneggar n Řɛahd n Jdid.  
\b  
\m  
\m Aɛuǧi i Yisem n AREBBI,  
\m Babatneɣ d Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ  
\m d Arruḥ Iqeddsen.   